ions-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions#在原討論中標記結果","content":"最理想的方式是回覆最初提問的話題，並在標題中包含 `已修正`、`已解決` 或其它含義明確的標記。在人來人往的郵件列表裡，一個看見討論串 `問題 X` 和 `問題 X - 已解決` 的潛在回覆者，會立刻明白自己不必再投入時間，除非他對這個問題本身感興趣。"},"8":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions#在原討論中標記結果","content":"這能節省社區的注意力，也能讓後來搜索相同問題的人直接找到結論。"},"9":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions#寫一個足夠有用的小結","content":"補充說明不必很長，也不必把整個過程複述一遍。簡單的一句 `你好，原來是網線出了問題！謝謝大家 - Bill`，也比什麼都不說要好。除非結論本身很有技術含量，否則簡短、明確的小結通常比長篇大論更有價值。"},"10":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions#寫一個足夠有用的小結","content":"一個好的結案回覆通常包含："},"11":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions-9","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions#寫一個足夠有用的小結","content":"最終確認的問題原因。"},"12":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions-10","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions#寫一個足夠有用的小結","content":"真正有效的解決辦法。"},"13":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions-11","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions#寫一個足夠有用的小結","content":"關鍵環境、版本或配置差異。"},"14":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions-12","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions#寫一個足夠有用的小結","content":"哪些猜測最終被排除。"},"15":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions-13","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions#寫一個足夠有用的小結","content":"對幫助者的感謝。"},"16":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions-14","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions#寫一個足夠有用的小結","content":"對於有深度的問題，張貼調試記錄摘要也很有幫助。先描述最終狀態和解決方案，**之後**再說明過程中有哪些可以避免的盲點。不要把結論寫成偵探小說；後來者最需要的是可檢索、可復現、可參考的答案。"},"17":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions-15","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions#把經驗留給後來者","content":"除了禮貌之外，這類補充還能幫助其他人在郵件列表、新聞群組、論壇或搜索引擎中找到真正解決問題的方案。你的結案回覆可能會在很長一段時間裡節省許多人的時間。"},"18":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions-16","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions#把經驗留給後來者","content":"如果這個問題暴露了文檔缺口、FAQ 缺失或教程誤導，請進一步想一想：是否可以補一段文檔、提交一個 FAQ 條目，或者向維護者發一個小補丁？這類後續行動往往比單純說“謝謝”更有價值。"},"19":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions-17","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions#讓幫助者看到結果","content":"至少，這種補充能讓每位參與協助的人從問題解決中得到滿足感。如果你自己不是技術專家，就相信我們：這種滿足感對那些自願幫助你的人非常重要。問題懸而未決會讓人灰心；看到問題被解決，會讓人願意繼續幫助下一個認真提問的人。"},"20":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions-18","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/after-questions#讓幫助者看到結果","content":"在黑客文化中，良好的後續行動不僅是禮貌，更是聲譽的一部分。你善待幫助過你的人，也是在為下一次獲得幫助積累信用。"},"21":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","type":"page","content":"在提問之前","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions"},"22":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#先自己找一輪答案","content":"先自己找一輪答案"},"23":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#讓別人看見你的努力","content":"讓別人看見你的努力"},"24":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#搜索不是形式而是縮小問題","content":"搜索不是形式，而是縮小問題"},"25":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#給問題一點冷卻時間","content":"給問題一點冷卻時間"},"26":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#避免帶著錯誤假設發問","content":"避免帶著錯誤假設發問"},"27":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#用行動換來答案","content":"用行動換來答案"},"28":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","content":"在你準備通過電子郵件、論壇、Issue 區、新聞群組或聊天室提出技術問題之前，請先停下來做一輪準備。提問不是把麻煩轉交給別人，而是把你已經觀察到的事實、已經嘗試過的路徑，以及仍然無法理解的部分整理出來，讓別人可以接著判斷。"},"29":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#先自己找一輪答案","content":"在發出問題之前，至少嘗試下面這些事情："},"30":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#先自己找一輪答案","content":"在你準備提問的論壇、郵件列表或 Issue 區中搜索舊文章。"},"31":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-9","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#先自己找一輪答案","content":"使用搜索引擎查找錯誤信息、關鍵日誌、異常名稱或具體行為。"},"32":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-10","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#先自己找一輪答案","content":"閱讀手冊、官方文檔、命令幫助或 API 說明。"},"33":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-11","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#先自己找一輪答案","content":"閱讀常見問題文件（FAQ）、故障排查指南和已知問題列表。"},"34":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-12","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#先自己找一輪答案","content":"自己做最小化檢查或實驗，確認問題是否能穩定復現。"},"35":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-13","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#先自己找一輪答案","content":"向身邊更有經驗的朋友、同事或同學請教。"},"36":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-14","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#先自己找一輪答案","content":"如果你是程序開發者，請閱讀相關源代碼、測試用例或變更記錄。"},"37":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-15","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#先自己找一輪答案","content":"這一步的目的不是證明你已經無所不知，而是儘量排除那些已經有明確答案、只需要耐心查找的問題。你先完成這輪工作，別人接手時才不必從最基礎的地方重新替你走一遍。"},"38":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-16","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#讓別人看見你的努力","content":"當你提出問題時，請主動說明你已經做過哪些嘗試。比如你搜索過哪些關鍵詞，讀過哪些文檔，嘗試過哪些配置，得到過哪些錯誤結果。這樣做能讓回答者知道，你並不是一個不勞而獲、隨手把問題丟給社區的人。"},"39":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-17","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#讓別人看見你的努力","content":"如果可以，請進一步說明你在這些嘗試中**學到了什麼**。例如："},"40":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-18","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#讓別人看見你的努力","content":"你發現問題只在某個版本出現。"},"41":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-19","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#讓別人看見你的努力","content":"你確認同一段配置在另一臺機器上可以工作。"},"42":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-20","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#讓別人看見你的努力","content":"你排除了權限、網絡、路徑或依賴版本中的某一類原因。"},"43":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-21","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#讓別人看見你的努力","content":"你找到過相似問題，但它的前提條件與你不同。"},"44":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-22","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#讓別人看見你的努力","content":"這些信息比一句“我試過了，沒用”有價值得多。它們能幫助別人快速判斷下一步該看哪裡，也能讓你的問題成為後來者可以搜索和複用的資料。"},"45":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-23","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#搜索不是形式而是縮小問題","content":"善用搜索引擎，尤其要搜索完整的錯誤信息、異常類型、關鍵日誌片段、命令輸出和庫版本號。對於歷史資料較多的技術，也可以搜索 Google 論壇、項目郵件列表、Issue 區和問答站點。"},"46":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-24","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#搜索不是形式而是縮小問題","content":"即使搜索沒有直接給出答案，也請把搜索過程寫進問題中。例如："},"47":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-25","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#搜索不是形式而是縮小問題","content":"`我用 Google 搜索過 \"exact error message here\"、\"library name version error\"，但找到的結果都針對舊版本，和我現在的環境不一致。`"},"48":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-26","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#搜索不是形式而是縮小問題","content":"這句話的價值不只是表明你努力過。它還告訴回答者哪些路徑已經走不通，避免他們重複給出你已經驗證過的建議。同時，包含搜索詞的問題也更容易被搜索引擎收錄，未來遇到相似問題的人更可能找到你的討論。"},"49":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-27","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#給問題一點冷卻時間","content":"彆著急，不要指望幾秒鐘的搜索就解決一個複雜問題。很多技術問題需要你多讀幾段文檔、多試幾個變量、多比較幾組現象，才能看清真正的矛盾在哪裡。"},"50":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-28","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#給問題一點冷卻時間","content":"在向專家求助之前，可以再做一次短暫覆盤："},"51":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-29","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#給問題一點冷卻時間","content":"我能否用一句話說清楚我想達到的目標？"},"52":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-30","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#給問題一點冷卻時間","content":"我能否穩定復現這個問題？"},"53":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-31","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#給問題一點冷卻時間","content":"我是否記錄了環境、版本、輸入、輸出和錯誤信息？"},"54":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-32","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#給問題一點冷卻時間","content":"我是否知道哪些因素已經被排除？"},"55":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-33","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#給問題一點冷卻時間","content":"我的問題是否只包含一個清晰的主題，而不是把許多無關問題混在一起？"},"56":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-34","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#給問題一點冷卻時間","content":"草率的問題通常只能得到草率的回答，甚至根本得不到回答。越能表現出你在求助前付出的閱讀、實驗和思考，你越有可能得到實質性的幫助。"},"57":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-35","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#避免帶著錯誤假設發問","content":"小心別問錯了問題。很多糟糕的問題並不是因為提問者不會描述現象，而是因為他們過早認定了原因。例如，問題明明可能是權限、路徑、版本衝突或輸入格式導致的，卻直接問“為什麼這個庫有 bug”。"},"58":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-36","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#避免帶著錯誤假設發問","content":"如果你的問題建立在錯誤假設上，回答者可能只能糾正你的假設，而不是給出你期待的答案。更好的做法是把事實和猜測分開："},"59":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-37","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#避免帶著錯誤假設發問","content":"事實：我執行了什麼命令，輸入是什麼，實際輸出是什麼。"},"60":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-38","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#避免帶著錯誤假設發問","content":"預期：我原本以為會發生什麼。"},"61":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-39","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#避免帶著錯誤假設發問","content":"猜測：我懷疑可能和某個配置有關，但還沒有證據。"},"62":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-40","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#避免帶著錯誤假設發問","content":"求助點：我應該繼續檢查哪一層？"},"63":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-41","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#避免帶著錯誤假設發問","content":"這樣寫能給回答者留下判斷空間，也能減少他們被迫拆解錯誤前提的成本。"},"64":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-42","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#用行動換來答案","content":"絕不要自以為**理應**得到答案。你沒有為社區成員的時間付費，也沒有資格要求別人無條件替你解決問題。你能得到答案，是靠自己提出有內涵、有邊界、有思考價值的問題去**掙到**的。"},"65":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-43","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#用行動換來答案","content":"這並不意味著你必須已經接近答案。相反，只要你表現出願意繼續行動，問題就更容易得到回應。下面這些問法通常比“請把完整步驟發給我”更有效："},"66":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-44","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#用行動換來答案","content":"`誰能給我一點排查方向？`"},"67":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-45","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#用行動換來答案","content":"`這個最小示例裡還缺了什麼關鍵信息？`"},"68":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-46","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#用行動換來答案","content":"`我應該優先檢查權限、依賴版本，還是輸入格式？`"},"69":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-47","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#用行動換來答案","content":"`我目前的推斷是否有明顯錯誤？`"},"70":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions-48","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/before-questions#用行動換來答案","content":"這些問法傳達了一件重要的事：只要有人能指出正確方向，你就願意繼續完成剩下的工作。對技術社區來說，這樣的提問者值得幫助。"},"71":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","type":"page","content":"好問題和壞問題","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question"},"72":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question#查找資料類問題","content":"查找資料類問題"},"73":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question#編譯失敗類問題","content":"編譯失敗類問題"},"74":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question#硬件或環境異常類問題","content":"硬件或環境異常類問題"},"75":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question#告訴我答案與指引我排查","content":"“告訴我答案”與“指引我排查”"},"76":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question#例子背後的教訓","content":"例子背後的教訓"},"77":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","content":"最後，我們通過幾個對照例子來說明什麼叫“聰明地提問”。同一個問題會以兩種方式出現：一種暴露出懶惰、傲慢或信息不足，另一種則展示了準備、邊界和可協作性。"},"78":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","content":"閱讀這些例子時，不要只記住句式。真正重要的是背後的判斷標準：你是否說明了目標，是否展示了嘗試，是否給出了環境，是否把責任推給別人，是否讓回答者有足夠的信息繼續分析。"},"79":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question#查找資料類問題","content":"**蠢問題**："},"80":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question#查找資料類問題","content":"> 我可以在哪兒找到關於 Foonly Flurbamatic 的資料？"},"81":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-9","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question#查找資料類問題","content":"這種問法無非想得到 STFW 這樣的回答。"},"82":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-10","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question#查找資料類問題","content":"**聰明問題**："},"83":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-11","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question#查找資料類問題","content":"> 我用 Google 搜索過 \"Foonly Flurbamatic 2600\"，但是沒找到有用的結果。誰知道上哪兒去找對這種設備編程的資料？"},"84":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-12","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question#查找資料類問題","content":"這個問題已經 STFW 過了，看起來他真的遇到了麻煩。"},"85":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-13","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question#編譯失敗類問題","content":"**蠢問題**："},"86":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-14","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question#編譯失敗類問題","content":"> 我從 foo 項目找來的源碼沒法編譯。它怎麼這麼爛？"},"87":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-15","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question#編譯失敗類問題","content":"他覺得都是別人的錯，這個傲慢自大的提問者。"},"88":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-16","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question#編譯失敗類問題","content":"**聰明問題**："},"89":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-17","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question#編譯失敗類問題","content":"> foo 項目代碼在 Nulix 6.2 版下無法編譯通過。我讀過了 FAQ，但裡面沒有提到跟 Nulix 有關的問題。這是我編譯過程的記錄，我有什麼做的不對的地方嗎？"},"90":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-18","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question#編譯失敗類問題","content":"提問者已經指明瞭環境，也讀過了 FAQ，還列出了錯誤，並且他沒有把問題的責任推到別人頭上，他的問題值得被關注。"},"91":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-19","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question#硬件或環境異常類問題","content":"**蠢問題**："},"92":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-20","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question#硬件或環境異常類問題","content":"> 我的主機板有問題了，誰來幫我？"},"93":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-21","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question#硬件或環境異常類問題","content":"某黑客對這類問題的回答通常是：`好的，還要幫你拍拍背和換尿布嗎？`，然後按下刪除鍵。"},"94":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-22","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question#硬件或環境異常類問題","content":"**聰明問題**："},"95":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-23","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question#硬件或環境異常類問題","content":"> 我在 S2464 主機板上試過了 X 、 Y 和 Z ，但沒什麼作用，我又試了 A 、 B 和 C 。請注意當我嘗試 C 時的奇怪現象。顯然 florbish 正在 grommicking，但結果出人意料。通常在 Athlon MP 主機板上引起 grommicking 的原因是什麼？有誰知道接下來我該做些什麼測試才能找出問題？"},"96":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-24","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question#硬件或環境異常類問題","content":"這個傢伙，從另一個角度來看，值得去回答他。他表現出瞭解決問題的能力，而不是坐等天上掉答案。"},"97":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-25","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question#告訴我答案與指引我排查","content":"在最後一個問題中，注意`告訴我答案`和`給我啟示，指出我還應該做什麼診斷工作`之間微妙而又重要的區別。"},"98":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-26","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question#告訴我答案與指引我排查","content":"事實上，後一個問題源自於 2001 年 8 月在 Linux 內核郵件列表（lkml）上的一個真實的提問。我（Eric）就是那個提出問題的人。我在 Tyan S2464 主板上觀察到了這種無法解釋的鎖定現象，列表成員們提供瞭解決這一問題的重要信息。"},"99":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-27","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question#告訴我答案與指引我排查","content":"通過我的提問方法，我給了別人可以咀嚼玩味的東西；我設法讓人們很容易參與並且被吸引進來。我顯示了自己具備和他們同等的能力，並邀請他們與我共同探討。通過告訴他們我所走過的彎路，以避免他們再浪費時間，我也表明了對他們寶貴時間的尊重。"},"100":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-28","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question#例子背後的教訓","content":"事後，當我向每個人表示感謝，並且讚賞這次良好的討論經歷的時候，一個 Linux 內核郵件列表的成員表示，他覺得我的問題得到解決並非由於我是這個列表中的**名**人，而是因為我用了正確的方式來提問。"},"101":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-29","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question#例子背後的教訓","content":"黑客從某種角度來說是擁有豐富知識但缺乏人情味的傢伙；我相信他是對的，如果我**像**個乞討者那樣提問，不論我是誰，一定會惹惱某些人或者被他們忽視。他建議我記下這件事，這直接導致了本指南的出現。"},"102":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question-30","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/good-or-bad-question#例子背後的教訓","content":"一個好問題不保證一定有人回答，但它會顯著提高別人願意投入時間的概率。它傳達的不是“替我完成工作”，而是“我已經做了該做的準備，現在需要更有經驗的人幫助我繼續判斷”。"},"103":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well","type":"page","content":"如何更好的回答問題","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well"},"104":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well#先假設對方可能只是緊張","content":"先假設對方可能只是緊張"},"105":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well#不確定時要誠實","content":"不確定時要誠實"},"106":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well#用反問幫助對方補齊信息","content":"用反問幫助對方補齊信息"},"107":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well#真要回答就認真回答","content":"真要回答，就認真回答"},"108":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well#讓社區從一次回答中受益","content":"讓社區從一次回答中受益"},"109":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well","content":"好的技術社區不只需要會提問的人，也需要會回答的人。回答問題時，你既是在解決一個具體問題，也是在示範社區如何思考、如何表達、如何維護質量。"},"110":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well#先假設對方可能只是緊張","content":"**態度和善一點。** 問題帶來的壓力常使人顯得無禮或愚蠢，但很多時候他們只是焦慮、困惑或缺乏經驗。"},"111":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well#先假設對方可能只是緊張","content":"**對初犯者私下回復。** 對那些坦誠犯錯的人，沒有必要當眾羞辱。一個真正的新手也許連怎麼搜索、該去哪裡找 FAQ、怎樣貼錯誤日誌都不知道。私下提醒能解決的問題，不必公開放大。"},"112":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well#不確定時要誠實","content":"**如果你不確定，一定要說出來！** 一個聽起來權威的錯誤回覆，比沒有回覆還糟。不要因為扮演專家很有趣，就給別人亂指路。謙虛和誠實能給提問者與旁觀者都樹立好榜樣。"},"113":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well-9","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well#不確定時要誠實","content":"**如果幫不了忙，也別妨礙他。** 不要在實際操作步驟上開玩笑。錯誤命令、偽造參數或危險建議可能會毀掉提問者的環境；總有人會把它們當成真的指令執行。"},"114":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well-10","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well#用反問幫助對方補齊信息","content":"**試探性的反問以引出更多細節。** 如果你做得好，提問者可以學到東西，你也可以。試著把一個粗糙問題引導成好問題：詢問版本、環境、復現步驟、完整錯誤信息、預期結果和已經嘗試過的路徑。"},"115":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well-11","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well#用反問幫助對方補齊信息","content":"儘管對懶惰問題抱怨一句 RTFM 有時是正當的，但給出文檔鏈接、FAQ 入口，甚至只是建議幾個更有效的搜索關鍵詞，通常會更有幫助。"},"116":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well-12","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well#真要回答就認真回答","content":"**如果你決定回答，就請給出好的答案。** 當別人正在使用錯誤工具或錯誤方法時，不要只給一個笨拙的權宜之計（workaround）。更好的回答是推薦合適的工具，重新界定問題，並解釋為什麼原方向不合適。"},"117":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well-13","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well#真要回答就認真回答","content":"**正面地回答問題。** 如果提問者已經深入研究，並說明試過 X、Y、Z、A、B、C 但沒有結果，回答 `試試看 A 或 B`，或者把同一組建議原樣貼回去並附一個鏈接，幾乎沒有價值。你應該基於他已經提供的信息繼續推進。"},"118":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well-14","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well#讓社區從一次回答中受益","content":"**幫助你的社區從問題中學習。** 當你回覆一個好問題時，可以問問自己：`如何修改相關文檔或 FAQ，才能避免以後反覆回答同樣的問題？` 如果答案明確，就向文檔維護者提交補丁或建議。"},"119":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well-15","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-answer-well#讓社區從一次回答中受益","content":"如果你是在研究一番後才作出回答，**展現你的技巧，而不是隻端出結果**。解釋你如何定位問題、如何排除可能性、為什麼選擇這個方案。畢竟，`授人以魚不如授人以漁`。"},"120":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser","type":"page","content":"如何避免扮演失敗者","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser"},"121":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser#被指出錯誤時先穩住","content":"被指出錯誤時先穩住"},"122":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser#分清不舒服和沒價值","content":"分清“不舒服”和“沒價值”"},"123":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser#遇到真正的攻擊怎麼辦","content":"遇到真正的攻擊怎麼辦"},"124":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser#不要捲入口水戰","content":"不要捲入口水戰"},"125":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser","content":"在黑客社區的論壇中，即使你已經努力遵循本指南，也可能有幾次搞砸。你可能會在公開場合被指出哪裡做錯了，而且語氣未必溫和。"},"126":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser#被指出錯誤時先穩住","content":"這種事發生以後，最糟糕的反應是哀嚎自己的遭遇、宣稱遭到攻擊、要求對方道歉、高聲尖叫、憋悶氣、威脅訴諸法律，或者跑去向對方的僱主投訴。相反，你應該先熬過去。"},"127":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser#被指出錯誤時先穩住","content":"這很正常。事實上，它對社區是有益且合理的。公開技術社區需要公開的標準，而標準不會自行維持，它們是通過參與者積極而**公開地**執行來維持的。"},"128":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser#被指出錯誤時先穩住","content":"不要堅持認為所有批評都應該通過私下郵件傳送。它通常不是這樣運作的。當有人指出你的說法有誤、問題描述不足或假設站不住腳時，把這類反饋一概理解為人身攻擊並沒有幫助。"},"129":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser#分清不舒服和沒價值","content":"也有一些論壇受過度禮節要求誤導，禁止參與者指出別人帖子裡的問題，並聲稱 `如果你不想幫助用戶就閉嘴。` 結果往往是有想法的參與者紛紛離開，留下毫無意義的嘮叨和低質量討論。"},"130":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser-9","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser#分清不舒服和沒價值","content":"誇張地說，你要的是這種表面“友善”，還是能真正解決問題的討論？兩個裡面通常只能挑一個。"},"131":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser-10","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser#分清不舒服和沒價值","content":"記住：當黑客說你搞砸了，並且告訴你不要再這樣做時，他通常是在關心**你**和**他的社區**。對他而言，完全忽略你、把你從自己的生活中過濾掉，反而更省事。如果你做不到感謝，至少要表現得有尊嚴，別把每一次刺耳反饋都當成別人必須照顧你的證明。"},"132":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser-11","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser#遇到真正的攻擊怎麼辦","content":"有時候，即使你沒有搞砸，或者只是在對方想象中搞砸了，也會有人無緣無故地攻擊你本人。在這種情況下，抱怨反而**真的**可能把問題搞砸。"},"133":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser-12","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser#遇到真正的攻擊怎麼辦","content":"這些來找麻煩的人，要麼是毫無辦法卻自以為是專家的傢伙，要麼是在測試你是否真的會失控。其他讀者通常會忽略他們，或用自己的方式處理他們。這些人在給自己製造麻煩，不一定需要你親自處理。"},"134":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser-13","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser#不要捲入口水戰","content":"最好不要理睬大多數口水戰。當然，在忽略之前，你需要先確認兩件事："},"135":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser-14","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser#不要捲入口水戰","content":"它確實只是口水戰，而不是指出了你真實的問題。"},"136":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser-15","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser#不要捲入口水戰","content":"它沒有把真正的答案或關鍵線索藏在刺耳表達後面。"},"137":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser-16","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-avoid-being-loser#不要捲入口水戰","content":"如果確認只是挑釁，就讓它過去。你越能把注意力放回事實、證據、復現步驟和解決方案上，就越不像一個失敗者。"},"138":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer","type":"page","content":"如果無法得到解答","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer"},"139":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer#不要立刻重複張貼","content":"不要立刻重複張貼"},"140":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer#換一個更合適的渠道","content":"換一個更合適的渠道"},"141":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer#接受付費支持也是正常選擇","content":"接受付費支持也是正常選擇"},"142":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer#重新整理後再回來","content":"重新整理後再回來"},"143":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer","content":"如果仍得不到回答，請不要以為我們覺得無法幫助你。有時只是看到你問題的人不知道答案罷了。沒有回應不代表你被忽視，雖然不可否認這種差別很難區分。"},"144":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer#不要立刻重複張貼","content":"總的來說，簡單地重複張貼問題是個很糟的點子。這會被視為無意義的喧鬧。有點耐心，知道答案的人可能生活在不同的時區，可能正在睡覺，也可能暫時沒有看到你的問題。"},"145":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer#不要立刻重複張貼","content":"也有可能，你的問題一開始就沒有組織好。與其原樣重發，不如先重新檢查標題、環境信息、復現步驟、錯誤輸出和你已經嘗試過的路徑。"},"146":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer#換一個更合適的渠道","content":"你可以通過其他渠道獲得幫助，而這些渠道通常更適合初學者。許多線上和本地用戶群組由熱情的軟件愛好者組成，他們未必親自寫過軟件，但很願意互相幫助，也更習慣回答入門問題。"},"147":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer#換一個更合適的渠道","content":"如果問題屬於特定發行版、硬件、商業軟件、雲服務或組織內部環境，也應該優先尋找對應的用戶群、供應商支持、官方論壇或本地社區。換渠道不是逃避，而是把問題送到更可能有人理解上下文的地方。"},"148":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer-9","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer#接受付費支持也是正常選擇","content":"另外，你也可以向商業公司尋求幫助，不論公司大還是小。別因為需要付費才能獲得幫助而感到沮喪。假如你的汽車發動機汽缸密封圈爆掉了，你會把車送到修車鋪，併為維修付費。軟件沒有花錢，並不意味著技術支持也必須永久免費。"},"149":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer-10","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer#接受付費支持也是正常選擇","content":"對於 Linux 這類大眾化軟件，每個開發者可能對應成千上萬名用戶。一個人不可能處理所有求助請求。即使你要為協助付費，和購買同類封閉軟件相比，成本通常也並不誇張；而且開源生態中的付費支持往往更直接、更透明。"},"150":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer-11","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/if-cannot-get-answer#重新整理後再回來","content":"如果你仍想在原社區繼續提問，請先改進問題本身，而不是機械重複。把你新增的發現、縮小後的範圍、排除過的原因、仍然卡住的地方寫清楚。一個經過重新整理的問題，遠比同一段文字的第二次、第三次張貼更值得回應。"},"151":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs","type":"page","content":"提問的智慧","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs"},"152":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs","content":"一份關於技術提問、求知姿態與協作倫理的閱讀指南。"},"153":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs#從哪裡開始","content":"從哪裡開始"},"154":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs","content":"這份文檔討論的不是“怎樣顯得禮貌”，而是怎樣把一個混亂的問題，整理成值得他人投入判斷的問題。"},"155":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs","content":"在技術社區裡，提問是一種協作邀請。你給出的事實越清楚，推理越誠實，邊界越分明，回答者就越容易與你站到同一張地圖前，判斷下一步該往哪裡走。"},"156":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs#從哪裡開始","content":"如果你第一次閱讀，可以先從“簡介”和“在提問之前”開始，理解技術社區為什麼如此看重準備工作。真正準備發問時，再進入“正在提問時”，逐項檢查你的標題、上下文、症狀、目標和嘗試。"},"157":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs#從哪裡開始","content":"如果你已經得到了回覆，也不要急著結束。後續的總結、感謝、歸檔和反饋，同樣會影響別人是否願意在下一次繼續幫助你。"},"158":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs#從哪裡開始","content":"<Card title=\"從簡介開始\" href=\"/zh-tw/docs/introduction\" description=\"理解這份指南背後的技術社區文化。\" />"},"159":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs#從哪裡開始","content":"<Card title=\"正在提問時\" href=\"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions\" description=\"把事實、症狀、目標與嘗試講清楚。\" />"},"160":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs#從哪裡開始","content":"<Card title=\"如何理解答案\" href=\"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer\" description=\"讀懂簡短、尖銳或不完整的回答。\" />"},"161":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction","type":"page","content":"簡介","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction"},"162":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction#為什麼提問方式很重要","content":"為什麼提問方式很重要"},"163":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction#什麼是好問題","content":"什麼是“好問題”？"},"164":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction#為什麼我們不喜歡差問題","content":"為什麼我們不喜歡“差問題”？"},"165":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction#我們理解你的角色但你也要理解我們的邊界","content":"我們理解你的角色，但你也要理解我們的邊界"},"166":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction#想得到解答那就學會如何提問","content":"想得到解答？那就學會如何提問"},"167":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction#最後","content":"最後"},"168":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction#為什麼提問方式很重要","content":"在黑客的世界裡，你能否得到一個有用、準確且迅速的答案，往往不取決於你問題的嚴重程度，而是你**如何提問**。換句話說，**會提問，才能真正得到幫助**。本指南正是為了幫助你學會提問的藝術，從而提高你獲取有效技術支持的概率。"},"169":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction#為什麼提問方式很重要","content":"如今，隨著開源（Open Source）軟件的蓬勃發展，越來越多的用戶不再依賴官方客服，而是通過郵件列表、論壇、Issue 區、IRC、Discord 等社區渠道向其他用戶尋求幫助。幸運的是，這些社區中有許多經驗豐富、樂於分享的人，願意提供近乎“黑客級別”的回答——甚至有時比開發者還專業。這是一件**好事**。"},"170":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction#為什麼提問方式很重要","content":"不過，要想讓這些人認真對待你的問題，你也必須表現出一定的基本素養。我們在本指南中推薦的方法，不僅適用於黑客社區，同樣適用於任何由資深用戶主導的技術社群。你對他人時間和認知的尊重，是你能否獲得幫助的第一步。"},"171":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction-9","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction#什麼是好問題","content":"黑客喜歡富有挑戰的問題、邏輯清晰的問題、能激發他們思維的問題。一個問題如果能引發深入的技術討論、揭示軟件設計的盲點，甚至帶來工具層面的改進，那麼它不僅是你的一次求助，更可能是一次對整個社區的饋贈。&#x2A;*“好問題！”** 是我們能給予他人的最高讚美之一。"},"172":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction-10","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction#什麼是好問題","content":"一個提出得當的問題，可以幫助他人更深入理解自己的系統或代碼，也可能揭示文檔中的遺漏與設計中的缺陷。這種問題，我們不但願意回答，還會樂在其中。"},"173":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction-11","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction#為什麼我們不喜歡差問題","content":"黑客群體常被人誤解為“對新手不友善”，但問題的關鍵並不是“你是不是新手”，而是你有沒有付出足夠的努力。"},"174":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction-12","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction#為什麼我們不喜歡差問題","content":"我們鄙視的是那些不願意動腦、不做任何嘗試、不搜索就伸手的人。他們一上來就說“XX 不能用，幫我解決”，連一句清晰的描述、環境信息都不提供。這些人只想索取，從不考慮反饋、總結、歸檔或貢獻。他們浪費了所有人的時間，我們稱他們為 `失敗者（loser）`，有時為了幽默也寫作 `luser`。"},"175":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction-13","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction#為什麼我們不喜歡差問題","content":"請記住，我們並不是職業客服。我們是因為熱愛技術而自願抽出寶貴時間來維護社區、分享知識的人。我們每天都可能收到幾十甚至上百個問題，不可能一一回答。為了效率和精神健康，我們必須對問題進行優先級篩選。你表現得像個 winner，你的問題才會被認真對待。"},"176":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction-14","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction#我們理解你的角色但你也要理解我們的邊界","content":"我們知道，大多數人使用計算機是為了完成自己的工作，而不是沉迷於技術細節。他們有其他的興趣、職業與生活目標，不願投入過多時間去研究底層原理。這很正常，我們完全接受這一點。"},"177":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction-15","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction#我們理解你的角色但你也要理解我們的邊界","content":"但這也意味著，如果你不願自己解決問題，那你可以通過簽約商業技術支持服務獲得幫助，而不是試圖免費獲得黑客社區的時間。"},"178":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction-16","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction#我們理解你的角色但你也要理解我們的邊界","content":"我們歡迎所有願意學習、尊重知識、尊重時間的人加入我們的文化。無知不可怕，願意成長的人隨時受到歡迎。但如果你不願思考，甚至拒絕學習，我們不會勉強你，只是也不會浪費時間在你身上。"},"179":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction-17","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction#想得到解答那就學會如何提問","content":"你不需要是專家，也不必裝作無所不知。你只需要展現出你正在努力思考、觀察現象、排查可能性，並且願意主動配合。你的問題應該具體、清晰、有條理；你應該展示你做過哪些嘗試；你應該在提問前搜索是否有相似問題已經解決。"},"180":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction-18","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction#想得到解答那就學會如何提問","content":"表現得像個 winner：**機敏、自信、條理清晰，具備基本邏輯思維，並尊重他人的時間**。哪怕你暫時遇到了瓶頸，只要方法得當，社區幾乎一定願意提供幫助。"},"181":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction-19","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction#最後","content":"如果你想為本指南提供反饋或提出改進建議，我們也歡迎。但請注意，這不是一份通用的“網絡禮儀”文檔，而是一份**針對技術社區有效提問方式的實戰指南**。我們通常不會接受那些無助於提升問題質量的建議。"},"182":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction-20","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction#最後","content":"你可以將建議發送至："},"183":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction-21","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction#最後","content":"01\\@rusin7.com"},"184":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction-22","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/introduction#最後","content":"讓我們共同努力，構建一個更加高效、友好、互助的技術社區。"},"185":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","type":"page","content":"一些不該問的問題","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask"},"186":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#把搜索任務直接丟給別人","content":"把搜索任務直接丟給別人"},"187":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#把手段誤當成目標","content":"把手段誤當成目標"},"188":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#不願閱讀基礎文檔","content":"不願閱讀基礎文檔"},"189":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#不願自己做最小實驗","content":"不願自己做最小實驗"},"190":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#沒有描述具體問題","content":"沒有描述具體問題"},"191":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#把平臺問題扔給不相關的人","content":"把平臺問題扔給不相關的人"},"192":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#指控基礎工具有問題卻沒有證據","content":"指控基礎工具有問題卻沒有證據"},"193":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#需要現場操作的問題","content":"需要現場操作的問題"},"194":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#請求非法或惡意行為","content":"請求非法或惡意行為"},"195":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-9","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#總結","content":"總結"},"196":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-10","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","content":"以下是幾個經典的糟糕問題，以及黑客沒有回答時心中可能會想的事情。它們的共同點不是“問題太簡單”，而是提問者沒有展示必要的準備、邊界和判斷。"},"197":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-11","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","content":"先看目錄，再看每個例子背後的原因："},"198":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-12","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","content":"問題：我能在哪找到 X 程序或 X 資源？"},"199":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-13","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","content":"問題：我怎樣用 X 做 Y？"},"200":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-14","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","content":"問題：如何設定我的 shell 提示？"},"201":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-15","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","content":"問題：我可以用 Bass-o-matic 文件轉換工具將 AcmeCorp 文件轉換為 TeX 格式嗎？"},"202":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-16","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","content":"問題：我的程序/設定/SQL 語句沒有用"},"203":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-17","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","content":"問題：我的 Windows 電腦有問題，你能幫我嗎？"},"204":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-18","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","content":"問題：我的程序不會動了，我認為系統工具 X 有問題"},"205":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-19","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","content":"問題：我在安裝 Linux（或者 X ）時有問題，你能幫我嗎？"},"206":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-20","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","content":"問題：我怎麼才能破解 root 帳號/竊取 OP 特權/讀別人的郵件呢？"},"207":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-21","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#把搜索任務直接丟給別人","content":"> 問題：我能在哪找到 X 程序或 X 資源？"},"208":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-22","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#把搜索任務直接丟給別人","content":"回答：就在我找到它的地方啊，白痴 —— 搜索引擎的那一頭。天哪！難道還有人不會用 Google 嗎？"},"209":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-23","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#把搜索任務直接丟給別人","content":"這類問題的問題在於，它沒有展示任何搜索或篩選過程。更好的問法應該說明你查過哪些關鍵詞、找到了哪些候選結果、為什麼它們不適用。"},"210":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-24","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#把手段誤當成目標","content":"> 問題：我怎樣用 X 做 Y？"},"211":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-25","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#把手段誤當成目標","content":"回答：如果你想解決的是 Y ，提問時別給出可能並不恰當的方法。這種問題說明提問者不但對 X 完全無知，也對 Y 要解決的問題糊塗，還被特定形勢禁錮了思維。最好忽略這種人，等他們把問題搞清楚了再說。"},"212":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-26","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#把手段誤當成目標","content":"如果你真正想解決的是 Y，就直接描述 Y 的目標、約束和上下文。也許 X 根本不是合適工具，過早限定手段只會讓回答者被迫沿著錯誤方向幫你。"},"213":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-27","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#不願閱讀基礎文檔","content":"> 問題：如何設定我的 shell 提示？？"},"214":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-28","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#不願閱讀基礎文檔","content":"回答：如果你有足夠的智慧提這個問題，你也該有足夠的智慧去 RTFM，然後自己去找出來。"},"215":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-29","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#不願閱讀基礎文檔","content":"這類問題通常可以從手冊、FAQ 或入門文檔裡直接找到答案。如果你已經閱讀過相關材料，請指出你卡住的具體段落，而不是把整件事交給別人重講一遍。"},"216":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-30","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#不願自己做最小實驗","content":"> 問題：我可以用 Bass-o-matic 文件轉換工具將 AcmeCorp 文件轉換為 TeX 格式嗎？"},"217":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-31","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#不願自己做最小實驗","content":"回答：試試看就知道了。如果你試過，你就知道了答案，就不用浪費我的時間了。"},"218":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-32","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#不願自己做最小實驗","content":"如果實驗成本很低，請先自己試。提問可以圍繞“為什麼這個實驗結果和預期不一致”，而不是要求別人替你做本該由你完成的確認。"},"219":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-33","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#沒有描述具體問題","content":"> 問題：我的「程序/設定/SQL 語句」沒有用"},"220":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-34","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#沒有描述具體問題","content":"回答：這不算是問題吧，我對要我問你二十個問題才找得出你真正問題的問題沒興趣 —— 我有更有意思的事要做呢。在看到這類問題的時候，我的反應通常不外如下三種"},"221":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-35","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#沒有描述具體問題","content":"你還有什麼要補充的嗎？"},"222":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-36","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#沒有描述具體問題","content":"真糟糕，希望你能搞定。"},"223":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-37","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#沒有描述具體問題","content":"這關我屁事？"},"224":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-38","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#沒有描述具體問題","content":"“沒有用”不是可診斷的信息。你需要說明你做了什麼、期望發生什麼、實際發生什麼、完整錯誤信息是什麼，以及你已經排除了哪些原因。"},"225":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-39","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#把平臺問題扔給不相關的人","content":"> 問題：我的 Windows 電腦有問題，你能幫我嗎？"},"226":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-40","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#把平臺問題扔給不相關的人","content":"回答：能啊，扔掉微軟的垃圾，換個像 Linux 或 BSD 的開源操作系統吧。"},"227":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-41","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#把平臺問題扔給不相關的人","content":"注意：如果程序有官方版 Windows 或者與 Windows 有互動（如 Samba），你**可以**問與 Windows 相關的問題，只是別對問題是由 Windows 操作系統而不是程序本身造成的回覆感到驚訝， 因為 Windows 一般來說實在太爛，這種說法通常都是對的。"},"228":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-42","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#把平臺問題扔給不相關的人","content":"關鍵不是“不能問 Windows”，而是要問對地方、問對範圍。與項目本身有關的問題可以問項目社區；純粹的系統使用問題則應找更合適的 Windows 支持渠道。"},"229":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-43","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#指控基礎工具有問題卻沒有證據","content":"> 問題：我的程序不會動了，我認為系統工具 X 有問題"},"230":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-44","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#指控基礎工具有問題卻沒有證據","content":"回答：你完全有可能是第一個注意到被成千上萬用戶反覆使用的系統調用與函數庫文件有明顯缺陷的人，更有可能的是你完全沒有根據。不同凡響的說法需要不同凡響的證據，當你這樣聲稱時，你必須有清楚而詳盡的缺陷說明文件作後盾。"},"231":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-45","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#指控基礎工具有問題卻沒有證據","content":"越是指向底層、通用、被大量使用的組件，就越需要嚴謹證據。先假設自己的環境、輸入、用法或理解可能有誤，再用最小復現和清晰日誌支持你的判斷。"},"232":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-46","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#需要現場操作的問題","content":"> 問題：我在安裝 Linux（或者 X ）時有問題，你能幫我嗎？"},"233":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-47","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#需要現場操作的問題","content":"回答：不能，我只有親自在你的電腦上動手才能找到毛病。還是去找你當地的 Linux 使用群組者尋求實際的指導吧（你能在這兒找到用戶群組的清單）。"},"234":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-48","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#需要現場操作的問題","content":"注意：如果安裝問題與某 Linux 的發行版有關，在它的郵件列表、論壇或本地用戶群組中提問也許是恰當的。此時，應描述問題的準確細節。在此之前，先用 `Linux` 和**所有**被懷疑的硬件作關鍵詞仔細搜索。"},"235":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-49","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#需要現場操作的問題","content":"安裝類問題常常依賴現場環境、硬件狀態和屏幕輸出。如果無法提供足夠細節，本地用戶群組、發行版社區或能遠程查看環境的支持渠道，通常更適合處理這類問題。"},"236":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-50","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#請求非法或惡意行為","content":"> 問題：我怎麼才能破解 root 帳號/竊取 OP 特權/讀別人的郵件呢？"},"237":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-51","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#請求非法或惡意行為","content":"回答：想要這樣做，說明了你是個卑鄙小人；想找個黑客幫你，說明你是個白痴！"},"238":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-52","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#請求非法或惡意行為","content":"不要把破壞、竊取、繞過授權或侵犯隱私包裝成“技術問題”。負責任的技術社區不會幫助你傷害別人，也不會為了展示技術能力而參與違法或不道德的行為。"},"239":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask-53","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/questions-you-cannot-ask#總結","content":"這些問題之所以糟糕，是因為它們把搜索、實驗、定義目標、提供證據和承擔責任都推給了回答者。真正值得問的問題，應該讓別人看到：你已經做了合理準備，現在只是在某個具體、清晰、可討論的點上需要幫助。"},"240":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/related-resource","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/related-resource","type":"page","content":"相關資源","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/related-resource"},"241":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/related-resource-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/related-resource","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/related-resource#基礎知識","content":"基礎知識"},"242":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/related-resource-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/related-resource","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/related-resource#發佈軟件或補丁","content":"發佈軟件或補丁"},"243":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/related-resource-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/related-resource","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/related-resource","content":"下面這些資源可以幫助你補齊技術背景。它們並不是提問模板，而是讓你更容易理解系統、網絡、軟件發佈與社區協作的基礎材料。"},"244":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/related-resource-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/related-resource","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/related-resource#基礎知識","content":"如果你需要個人電腦、Unix 系統和網絡如何運作的基礎知識，參閱 Unix 系統和網絡基本原理。"},"245":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/related-resource-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/related-resource","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/related-resource#基礎知識","content":"閱讀這類材料的意義在於：當你能說清楚文件系統、進程、網絡連接、權限、標準輸入輸出等基本概念時，你的問題會更準確，回答者也更容易判斷你卡在哪一層。"},"246":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/related-resource-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/related-resource","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/related-resource#發佈軟件或補丁","content":"當你發佈軟件或補丁時，試著按軟件發佈實踐操作。"},"247":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/related-resource-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/related-resource","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/related-resource#發佈軟件或補丁","content":"良好的發佈習慣能減少他人使用、測試和反饋時的成本。版本號、變更記錄、構建方式、依賴說明和已知問題寫得越清楚，別人越容易給出有效反饋。"},"248":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/statement","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/statement","type":"page","content":"引言","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/statement"},"249":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/statement-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/statement","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/statement#這不是技術支持入口","content":"這不是技術支持入口"},"250":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/statement-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/statement","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/statement#為什麼必須說清楚","content":"為什麼必須說清楚"},"251":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/statement-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/statement","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/statement#你應該去哪裡提問","content":"你應該去哪裡提問"},"252":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/statement-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/statement","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/statement#最後提醒","content":"最後提醒"},"253":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/statement-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/statement","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/statement","content":"本指南自發布以來，得到了廣泛的引用和傳播。我們注意到，許多開源項目和工具在它們的官方網站或幫助文檔中都鏈接了本指南，這是非常值得鼓勵的行為——這正是我們設計和撰寫本指南的初衷之一：幫助用戶學習如何更有效地尋求技術支持。"},"254":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/statement-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/statement","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/statement#這不是技術支持入口","content":"然而，我們必須強調一個極為重要的事實："},"255":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/statement-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/statement","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/statement#這不是技術支持入口","content":"> **本指南不提供任何特定項目的實際支持服務！**"},"256":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/statement-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/statement","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/statement#這不是技術支持入口","content":"如果你是某個項目的管理員，並希望在你項目的網站或文檔中引用本指南，請務必在鏈接的顯著位置加上這一聲明。不要假設用戶會自動明白這點——現實是：他們不會。"},"257":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/statement-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/statement","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/statement#為什麼必須說清楚","content":"我們之所以如此強調這一點，是因為我們已經親身體驗到了未加聲明所帶來的後果：我們不斷地接到來自世界各地的請求，這些請求通常毫無頭緒、語焉不詳，甚至理所當然地認為我們負責解決他們遇到的所有技術問題。顯然，這完全不是我們所願意承擔的責任。"},"258":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/statement-9","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/statement","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/statement#為什麼必須說清楚","content":"請理解，我們撰寫本指南的目的，是為了教會你如何更有禮貌、更高效、更理性地向真正瞭解你所用軟件或硬件的人尋求幫助。在絕大多數（我們估計是 &#x2A;*99%**）情況下，那些人都不是我們。"},"259":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/statement-10","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/statement","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/statement#你應該去哪裡提問","content":"如果你現在正在閱讀這本指南，是因為你在某個項目中遇到了問題，並希望獲得幫助，那麼請仔細想一想：你真的認為本指南的作者就剛好是那個項目的維護者、開發者或技術支持嗎？我們很可能完全不知道你遇到的問題是關於什麼的。如果你看完本指南之後，仍然直接跑來找我們提問，那你很可能正是我們前面所說的那類人——**我們並不想與你交流的那類人**。"},"260":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/statement-11","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/statement","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/statement#你應該去哪裡提問","content":"我們不會回答你的問題。我們會忽略它們。我們希望你從這本指南中獲得的，是尋求真正有效幫助的能力，而不是錯誤地把我們當作“萬能客服”的聯繫方式。"},"261":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/statement-12","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/statement","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/statement#你應該去哪裡提問","content":"請去項目自己的 Issue 區、論壇、郵件列表、聊天室、用戶群組或商業支持渠道提問。那裡才有熟悉具體軟件、硬件、環境和歷史背景的人。"},"262":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/statement-13","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/statement","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/statement#最後提醒","content":"請記住：&#x2A;*尊重別人的時間，是你能獲得幫助的第一步。**"},"263":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/thanks","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/thanks","type":"page","content":"致謝","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/thanks"},"264":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/thanks-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/thanks","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/thanks#貢獻者","content":"貢獻者"},"265":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/thanks-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/thanks","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/thanks#為什麼保留致謝","content":"為什麼保留致謝"},"266":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/thanks-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/thanks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/thanks","content":"這份指南不是憑空完成的。許多人的反饋、例子和修訂建議，讓它從一篇關於提問方式的文章，逐漸變成一份更完整的技術社區協作指南。"},"267":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/thanks-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/thanks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/thanks#貢獻者","content":"Evelyn Mitchel 貢獻了一些愚蠢問題例子，並啟發了 `如何更好地回答問題` 這一節的編寫。"},"268":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/thanks-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/thanks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/thanks#貢獻者","content":"Mikhail Ramendik 貢獻了一些特別有價值的建議和改進。"},"269":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/thanks-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/thanks","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/thanks#為什麼保留致謝","content":"技術社區依賴持續的修正和補充。把貢獻者記錄下來，不只是禮貌，也是在提醒讀者：好的文檔和好的問題一樣，都是多人協作、反覆打磨的結果。"},"270":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive","type":"page","content":"處理無禮的回應","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧","如何理解答案"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive"},"271":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive#先判斷是否只是直接","content":"先判斷是否只是直接"},"272":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive#真正越界時也要有根據","content":"真正越界時也要有根據"},"273":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive#關於古怪行為的一種解釋","content":"關於“古怪行為”的一種解釋"},"274":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive#回到你真正想要的東西","content":"回到你真正想要的東西"},"275":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive","content":"很多黑客圈子中看似無禮的行為並不是存心冒犯。相反，它是直截了當，一針見血式的交流風格，這種風格更注重解決問題，而不是使人感覺舒服而卻模模糊糊。"},"276":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive#先判斷是否只是直接","content":"如果你覺得被冒犯了，試著平靜地反應。如果有人真的做了出格的事，郵件列表、新聞群組或論壇中的前輩多半會招呼他。如果這**沒有**發生而你卻發火了，那麼你發火對象的言語可能在黑客社區中看起來是正常的，而**你**將被視為有錯的一方，這將傷害到你獲取信息或幫助的機會。"},"277":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive#先判斷是否只是直接","content":"刺耳不一定等於無禮。很多技術反饋會直接指出錯誤、遺漏、重複問題或錯誤假設。先看裡面是否包含有用信息，再決定是否需要回應語氣本身。"},"278":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive#真正越界時也要有根據","content":"另一方面，你偶爾真的會碰到無禮和無聊的言行。與上述相反，對真正的冒犯者狠狠地打擊，用犀利的語言將其駁得體無完膚都是可以接受的。然而，在行事之前一定要非常非常的有根據。糾正無禮的言論與開始一場毫無意義的口水戰僅一線之隔，黑客們自己莽撞地越線的情況並不鮮見。如果你是新手或外人，避開這種莽撞的機會並不高。如果你想得到的是信息而不是消磨時光，這時最好不要把手放在鍵盤上以免冒險。"},"279":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive#真正越界時也要有根據","content":"如果你的目標是解決問題，很多時候最有效的做法是忽略語氣，抓住技術線索繼續推進。公開爭執會迅速消耗討論的注意力，也可能讓願意幫你的人離開。"},"280":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive-9","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive#關於古怪行為的一種解釋","content":"（有些人斷言很多黑客都有輕度的自閉症或亞斯伯格綜合症，缺少用於潤滑人類社會**正常**交往所需的神經。這既可能是真也可能是假的。如果你自己不是黑客，興許你認為我們腦袋有問題還能幫助你應付我們的古怪行為。只管這麼幹好了，我們不在乎。我們**喜歡**我們現在這個樣子，並且通常對病患標記都有站得住腳的懷疑。）"},"281":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive-10","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive#關於古怪行為的一種解釋","content":"Jeff Bigler 的觀察總結和這個相關也值得一讀 (**tact filters**)。"},"282":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive-11","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive#回到你真正想要的東西","content":"在下一節，我們會談到另一個問題，當**你**行為不當時所會受到的`冒犯`。"},"283":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive-12","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/Deal-with-offensive#回到你真正想要的東西","content":"在多數情況下，你來社區是為了獲得信息、解決問題、學習判斷，而不是贏得一場情緒爭執。把注意力放回事實、證據和下一步行動上，通常是收益最高的選擇。"},"284":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand","type":"page","content":"如果還是搞不懂","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧","如何理解答案"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand"},"285":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand#先消化再追問","content":"先消化，再追問"},"286":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand#糟糕追問和好追問","content":"糟糕追問和好追問"},"287":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand#追問也要繼續提供信息","content":"追問也要繼續提供信息"},"288":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand","content":"如果你看不懂回應，別立刻要求對方解釋。像你以前試著自己解決問題時那樣（利用手冊，FAQ，網絡，身邊的高手），先試著去搞懂他的回應。如果你真的需要對方解釋，記得表現出你已經從中學到了點什麼。"},"289":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand#先消化再追問","content":"回答者給你的可能只是一個關鍵詞、一個方向或一個判斷。你需要先圍繞這個線索做基本功：查手冊、讀 FAQ、搜索舊討論、試驗命令或詢問身邊更熟悉的人。"},"290":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand#先消化再追問","content":"如果你真的需要對方繼續解釋，請展示你已經做過的這一步。這樣對方知道你不是把下一輪思考也推回給他。"},"291":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand#糟糕追問和好追問","content":"比方說，如果我回答你：`看來似乎是 zentry 卡住了；你應該先清除它。`"},"292":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand#糟糕追問和好追問","content":"這是一個**很糟的**後續回應："},"293":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand#糟糕追問和好追問","content":"`zentry 是什麼？`"},"294":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand-9","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand#糟糕追問和好追問","content":"更好的問法是："},"295":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand-10","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand#糟糕追問和好追問","content":"`哦，我看過說明了，但是隻有 -z 和 -p 兩個參數中提到了 zentries，而且還都沒有清楚解釋如何清除它。你是指這兩個中的哪一個嗎？還是我看漏了什麼？`"},"296":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand-11","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/if-still-not-understand#追問也要繼續提供信息","content":"好的追問會說明三件事：你讀了什麼、你理解到了哪裡、你具體卡在哪個點。這樣別人只需要糾正你的理解或補充缺失部分，而不必重新從零開始教你。"},"297":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer","type":"page","content":"如何理解答案","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧","如何理解答案"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer"},"298":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer#回答不一定會像教程","content":"回答不一定會像教程"},"299":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer#閱讀答案時先做三件事","content":"閱讀答案時先做三件事"},"300":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer#本章會講什麼","content":"本章會講什麼"},"301":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer","content":"得到回答之後，真正的工作還沒有結束。你需要讀懂回答者給出的線索，判斷哪些內容是直接答案，哪些內容是在要求你繼續閱讀、搜索、補充信息或修正自己的假設。"},"302":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer#回答不一定會像教程","content":"技術社區裡的回答常常很短，也可能很直接。它們不一定會把背景知識重新講一遍，而是指向手冊、關鍵詞、錯誤位置或下一步排查方向。你要學會從這些提示中繼續推進，而不是期待別人把完整學習路徑鋪好。"},"303":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer#閱讀答案時先做三件事","content":"找出回答者指出的具體線索，例如文檔章節、命令、錯誤原因或關鍵詞。"},"304":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer#閱讀答案時先做三件事","content":"自己先閱讀、搜索和驗證，不要立刻要求對方展開講解。"},"305":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer#閱讀答案時先做三件事","content":"如果仍然不懂，再帶著你新學到的內容繼續追問。"},"306":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer#本章會講什麼","content":"本章會說明如何理解 `RTFM`、`STFW` 這類簡短回應，如何在仍然不懂時繼續追問，以及如何處理看起來刺耳甚至無禮的回覆。"},"307":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw","type":"page","content":"RTFM 和 STFW","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧","如何理解答案"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw"},"308":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw#這通常不是拒絕幫助","content":"這通常不是拒絕幫助"},"309":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw#你應該怎麼做","content":"你應該怎麼做"},"310":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw","content":"有一個古老而神聖的傳統：如果你收到`RTFM（Read The Fucking Manual）`的回應，回答者認為你**應該去讀他媽的手冊**。當然，基本上他是對的，你應該去讀一讀。"},"311":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw","content":"RTFM 有一個年輕的親戚。如果你收到`STFW（Search The Fucking Web）`的回應，回答者認為你**應該到他媽的網上搜索**。那人多半也是對的，去搜索一下吧。（更溫和一點的說法是 **Google 是你的朋友**！）"},"312":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw#這通常不是拒絕幫助","content":"在論壇，你也可能被要求去爬爬論壇的舊文。事實上，有人甚至可能熱心地為你提供以前解決此問題的討論串。但不要依賴這種關照，提問前應該先搜索一下舊文。"},"313":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw#這通常不是拒絕幫助","content":"通常，用這兩句之一回答你的人會給你一份包含你需要內容的手冊或者一個網址，而且他們打這些字的時候也正在讀著。這些答覆意味著回答者認為："},"314":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw#這通常不是拒絕幫助","content":"**你需要的信息非常容易獲得**；"},"315":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw#這通常不是拒絕幫助","content":"**你自己去搜索這些信息比灌給你，能讓你學到更多**。"},"316":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw#你應該怎麼做","content":"收到這類回覆後，正確反應不是生氣，而是順著線索去讀。打開手冊，搜索關鍵詞，翻舊討論，確認答案是否已經在那裡。如果你讀完仍然不懂，再帶著具體卡點回來提問。"},"317":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw-9","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw#你應該怎麼做","content":"例如，不要回 `我看不懂`，而要回：`我讀了手冊裡關於 X 的段落，但不確定這裡的 Y 是否就是你說的原因；我理解得對嗎？`"},"318":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw-10","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/how-to-read-answer/rtfm-and-stfw#你應該怎麼做","content":"你不應該因此不爽；**依照黑客的標準，他已經表示了對你一定程度的關注，而沒有對你的要求視而不見**。你應該對他祖母般的慈祥表示感謝。"},"319":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum","type":"page","content":"慎選提問的論壇","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧","正在提問時"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum"},"320":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum#發錯地方會發生什麼","content":"發錯地方會發生什麼"},"321":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum#先找到真正相關的社區","content":"先找到真正相關的社區"},"322":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum#先觀察社區文化","content":"先觀察社區文化"},"323":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum#確認問題屬於這裡","content":"確認問題屬於這裡"},"324":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum#不要濫用私人渠道","content":"不要濫用私人渠道"},"325":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum","content":"選擇提問場合，是提問質量的一部分。一個問題即使描述得很好，發錯地方也可能被忽略；而一個普通問題如果發到合適的社區，反而更容易得到準確回應。"},"326":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum#發錯地方會發生什麼","content":"小心選擇你要提問的場合。如果你做了下面這些事，很可能會被忽略，或者被看作失敗者："},"327":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum#發錯地方會發生什麼","content":"在與主題不合的論壇上貼出你的問題。"},"328":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum#發錯地方會發生什麼","content":"在探討進階技術問題的論壇張貼非常初級的問題；反之亦然。"},"329":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum-9","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum#發錯地方會發生什麼","content":"在太多的不同新聞群組上重複轉貼同樣的問題（cross-post）。"},"330":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum-10","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum#發錯地方會發生什麼","content":"向既非熟人也沒有義務解決你問題的人發送私人電郵。"},"331":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum-11","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum#發錯地方會發生什麼","content":"黑客會剔除掉那些搞錯場合的問題，以保護他們溝通的渠道不被無關的東西淹沒。你不會想讓這種事發生在自己身上的。"},"332":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum-12","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum#先找到真正相關的社區","content":"因此，第一步是找到對的論壇。再說一次，Google 和其它搜索引擎還是你的朋友，用它們來找到與你遭遇到困難的軟硬件問題最相關的網站。通常那兒都有常見問題（FAQ）、郵件列表及相關說明文件的鏈接。如果你的努力（包括**閱讀** FAQ）都沒有結果，網站上也許還有報告 Bug（Bug-reporting）的流程或鏈接，如果是這樣，鏈過去看看。"},"333":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum-13","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum#先找到真正相關的社區","content":"向陌生的人或論壇發送郵件最可能是風險最大的事情。舉例來說，別假設一個提供豐富內容的網頁的作者會想充當你的免費顧問。不要對你的問題是否會受到歡迎做太樂觀的估計 —— 如果你不確定，那就向別處發送，或者壓根別發。"},"334":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum-14","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum#先觀察社區文化","content":"在選擇論壇、新聞群組或郵件列表時，別太相信它的名字，先看看 FAQ 或者許可書以弄清楚你的問題是否切題。發文前先翻翻已有的話題，這樣可以讓你感受一下那裡的文化。事實上，事先在新聞組或郵件列表的歷史記錄中搜索與你問題相關的關鍵詞是個極好的主意，也許這樣就找到答案了。即使沒有，也能幫助你歸納出更好的問題。"},"335":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum-15","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum#先觀察社區文化","content":"別像機關槍似的一次“掃射”所有的幫助渠道，這就像大喊大叫一樣會使人不快。要一個一個地來。"},"336":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum-16","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum#確認問題屬於這裡","content":"搞清楚你的主題！最典型的錯誤之一是在某種致力於跨平臺可移植的語言、套件或工具的論壇中提關於 Unix 或 Windows 操作系統程序界面的問題。如果你不明白為什麼這是大錯，最好在搞清楚這之間差異之前什麼也別問。"},"337":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum-17","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum#確認問題屬於這裡","content":"一般來說，在仔細挑選的公共論壇中提問，會比在私有論壇中提同樣的問題更容易得到有用的回答。有幾個理由可以支持這點，一是看潛在的回覆者有多少，二是看觀眾有多少。黑客較願意回答那些能幫助到許多人的問題。"},"338":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum-18","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum#不要濫用私人渠道","content":"可以理解的是，老練的黑客和一些熱門軟件的作者正在接受過多的錯發信息。就像那根最後壓垮駱駝背的稻草一樣，你的加入也有可能使情況走向極端 —— 已經好幾次了，一些熱門軟件的作者由於湧入其私人郵箱的大量不堪忍受的無用郵件而不再提供支持。"},"339":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum-19","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/carefully-select-forum#不要濫用私人渠道","content":"除非對方明確邀請你私下聯繫，否則優先使用公共渠道。公共討論不僅更容易得到回答，也能讓後來遇到同樣問題的人受益。"},"340":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question","type":"page","content":"明確表達你的問題以及需求","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧","正在提問時"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question"},"341":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question#明確你希望別人做什麼","content":"明確你希望別人做什麼"},"342":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question#尊重專家最稀缺的資源","content":"尊重專家最稀缺的資源"},"343":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question#簡化問題不等於隱藏信息","content":"簡化問題不等於隱藏信息"},"344":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question","content":"漫無邊際的提問是近乎無休無止的時間黑洞。最有可能給你有用答案的人通常也正是最忙的人（他們忙是因為要親自完成大部分工作）。這樣的人對無節制的時間黑洞相當厭惡，所以他們也傾向於厭惡那些漫無邊際的提問。"},"345":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question#明確你希望別人做什麼","content":"如果你明確表述需要回答者做什麼（如提供指點、發送一段代碼、檢查你的補丁、或是其他等等），就最有可能得到有用的答案。因為這會定出一個時間和精力的上限，便於回答者能集中精力來幫你。這麼做很棒。"},"346":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question#明確你希望別人做什麼","content":"你可以明確請求："},"347":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question#明確你希望別人做什麼","content":"幫你判斷下一步排查方向。"},"348":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question#明確你希望別人做什麼","content":"檢查一個最小復現示例。"},"349":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question#明確你希望別人做什麼","content":"看看補丁思路是否合理。"},"350":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question-9","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question#明確你希望別人做什麼","content":"指出相關文檔或關鍵概念。"},"351":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question-10","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question#明確你希望別人做什麼","content":"判斷錯誤信息是否指向某類常見原因。"},"352":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question-11","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question#明確你希望別人做什麼","content":"這些請求都有邊界。它們不會要求別人無期限地接管你的問題。"},"353":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question-12","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question#尊重專家最稀缺的資源","content":"要理解專家們所處的世界，請把專業技能想像為充裕的資源，而回復的時間則是稀缺的資源。你要求他們奉獻的時間越少，你越有可能從真正專業而且很忙的專家那裡得到解答。"},"354":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question-13","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question#尊重專家最稀缺的資源","content":"因此，你的問題應該讓回答者能快速決定：我是否懂這個問題，我需要看哪些信息，我能否在幾分鐘內給出方向。"},"355":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question-14","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question#簡化問題不等於隱藏信息","content":"所以，界定一下你的問題，使專家花在辨識你的問題和回答所需要付出的時間減到最少，這技巧對你獲得有用的答案相當有幫助 —— 但這技巧通常和簡化問題有所區別。因此，問`我想更好地理解 X，可否指點一下哪有好一點說明？`通常比問`你能解釋一下 X 嗎？`更好。如果你的代碼不能運作，通常請別人看看哪裡有問題，比要求別人替你改正要明智得多。"},"356":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question-15","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/clearly-express-your-question#簡化問題不等於隱藏信息","content":"好的提問會把問題縮小到一個可處理的範圍，但不會刪掉診斷所需的關鍵事實。你要減少的是噪聲，而不是證據。"},"357":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing","type":"page","content":"禮多人不怪","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧","正在提問時"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing"},"358":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing#禮貌不能替代內容","content":"禮貌不能替代內容"},"359":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing#禮貌會影響長期回應","content":"禮貌會影響長期回應"},"360":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing#關於先謝了","content":"關於“先謝了”"},"361":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing","content":"彬彬有禮，多用`請`和`謝謝您的關注`，或`謝謝你的關照`。讓大家都知道你對他們花時間免費提供幫助心存感激。"},"362":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing#禮貌不能替代內容","content":"坦白說，這一點並沒有比使用清晰、正確、精準且合乎語法和避免使用專用格式重要（也不能取而代之）。黑客們一般寧可讀有點唐突但技術上鮮明的 Bug 報告，而不是那種有禮但含糊的報告。（如果這點讓你不解，記住我們是按問題能教給我們什麼來評價問題的價值的）"},"363":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing#禮貌不能替代內容","content":"也就是說，禮貌是加分項，不是遮羞布。一個沒有環境、沒有錯誤信息、沒有嘗試記錄的問題，哪怕寫滿“麻煩您了”，也仍然是一個難以回答的問題。"},"364":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing#禮貌會影響長期回應","content":"然而，如果你有一串的問題待解決，客氣一點肯定會增加你得到有用回應的機會。"},"365":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing#禮貌會影響長期回應","content":"技術社區是有記憶的。別人會記得你是否尊重時間、是否反饋結果、是否在得到幫助後補充總結。客氣、誠實、及時感謝，會讓人更願意在下一次繼續理你。"},"366":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing#關於先謝了","content":"（我們注意到，自從本指南發佈後，從資深黑客那裡得到的唯一嚴重缺陷反饋，就是對預先道謝這一條。一些黑客覺得`先謝了`意味著事後就不用再感謝任何人的暗示。我們的建議是要麼先說`先謝了`，**然後**事後再對回覆者表示感謝，或者換種方式表達感激，譬如用`謝謝你的關注`或`謝謝你的關照`。）"},"367":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing-9","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/courtesy-costs-nothing#關於先謝了","content":"最穩妥的做法是：提問時表達對他人關注的感謝，問題解決後再明確感謝具體幫助你的人，並補充最終結果。"},"368":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process","type":"page","content":"描述目標而不是過程","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧","正在提問時"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process"},"369":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process#為什麼目標比步驟更重要","content":"為什麼目標比步驟更重要"},"370":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process#反例只問卡住的步驟","content":"反例：只問卡住的步驟"},"371":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process#好例子先說明真正目標","content":"好例子：先說明真正目標"},"372":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process#寫法建議","content":"寫法建議"},"373":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process","content":"如果你想弄清楚如何做某事（而不是報告一個 Bug），在開頭就描述你的目標，然後才陳述重現你所卡住的特定步驟。"},"374":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process#為什麼目標比步驟更重要","content":"經常尋求技術幫助的人在心中有個更高層次的目標，而他們在自以為能達到目標的特定道路上被卡住了，然後跑來問該怎麼走，但沒有意識到這條路本身就有問題。結果要費很大的勁才能搞定。"},"375":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process#為什麼目標比步驟更重要","content":"如果你只問某一步怎麼做，回答者只能幫你修補這一步；如果你說明真正目標，回答者可能會指出更簡單、更穩妥、更符合工具設計的方案。"},"376":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process#反例只問卡住的步驟","content":"**蠢問題：**"},"377":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process#反例只問卡住的步驟","content":"> 我怎樣才能從某繪圖程序的顏色選擇器中取得十六進制的 RGB 值？"},"378":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process-9","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process#好例子先說明真正目標","content":"**聰明問題：**"},"379":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process-10","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process#好例子先說明真正目標","content":"> 我正試著用替換一幅圖片的色碼（color table）成自己選定的色碼，我現在知道的唯一方法是編輯每個色碼區塊（table slot），\n> 但卻無法從某繪圖程序的顏色選擇器取得十六進制的 RGB 值。"},"380":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process-11","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process#好例子先說明真正目標","content":"第二種提問法比較聰明，因為它讓回答者知道你真正想完成的是修改圖片色碼，而不是單純獲取某個顏色值。你可能得到像是 `建議採用另一個更合適的工具` 這樣的回覆。"},"381":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process-12","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process#寫法建議","content":"可以用這樣的順序組織問題："},"382":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process-13","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process#寫法建議","content":"我最終想達到什麼結果。"},"383":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process-14","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process#寫法建議","content":"我目前選擇了什麼方法。"},"384":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process-15","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process#寫法建議","content":"我卡在這個方法的哪一步。"},"385":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process-16","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process#寫法建議","content":"我是否接受換一種方法。"},"386":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process-17","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-goal-not-process#寫法建議","content":"最後一點尤其重要。很多時候，最好的答案不是把你從錯誤路徑上繼續往前推，而是幫你換一條更合適的路。"},"387":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses","type":"page","content":"描述問題症狀而非你的猜測","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧","正在提問時"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses"},"388":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses#先給證據再給猜測","content":"先給證據，再給猜測"},"389":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses#反例過早下結論","content":"反例：過早下結論"},"390":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses#好例子描述可觀察現象","content":"好例子：描述可觀察現象"},"391":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses#讓我看看","content":"“讓我看看”"},"392":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses","content":"告訴黑客們你認為問題是怎樣造成的並沒什麼幫助。（如果你的推斷如此有效，還用向別人求助嗎？），因此要確信你原原本本告訴了他們問題的症狀，而不是你的解釋和理論；讓黑客們來推測和診斷。如果你認為陳述自己的猜測很重要，清楚地說明這只是你的猜測，並描述為什麼它們不起作用。"},"393":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses#先給證據再給猜測","content":"事實應該放在前面：發生了什麼、什麼時候發生、如何復現、錯誤信息是什麼、你觀察到哪些規律。猜測可以寫，但要標明它只是猜測，不要把它包裝成結論。"},"394":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses#反例過早下結論","content":"**蠢問題：**"},"395":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses#反例過早下結論","content":"> 我在編譯內核時接連遇到 SIG11 錯誤，\n> 我懷疑某條飛線搭在主板的走線上了，這種情況應該怎樣檢查最好？"},"396":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses#反例過早下結論","content":"這個問題把注意力引向了一個未經證實的硬件猜測，反而隱藏了真正有診斷價值的現象。"},"397":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses-9","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses#好例子描述可觀察現象","content":"**聰明問題：**"},"398":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses-10","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses#好例子描述可觀察現象","content":"> 我的組裝電腦是 FIC-PA2007 主機板搭載 AMD K6/233 CPU（威盛 Apollo VP2 芯片組），\n> 256MB Corsair PC133 SDRAM 內存，在編譯內核時，從開機 20 分鐘以後就頻頻產生 SIG11 錯誤，\n> 但是在頭 20 分鐘內從沒發生過相同的問題。重新啟動也沒有用，但是關機一晚上就又能工作 20 分鐘。\n> 所有內存都換過了，沒有效果。相關部分的標準編譯記錄如下…"},"399":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses-11","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses#好例子描述可觀察現象","content":"這裡的價值在於，它提供了硬件環境、時間規律、已做排除和相關日誌。回答者可以基於事實繼續診斷，而不是被迫先拆掉提問者的猜測。"},"400":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses-12","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/describe-symptoms-not-guesses#讓我看看","content":"由於以上這點似乎讓許多人覺得難以配合，這裡有句話可以提醒你：`所有的診斷專家都來自密蘇里州。` 美國國務院的官方座右銘則是：`讓我看看`（出自國會議員 Willard D. Vandiver 在 1899 年時的講話：`我來自一個出產玉米，棉花，牛蒡和民主黨人的國家，滔滔雄辯既不能說服我，也不會讓我滿意。我來自密蘇里州，你必須讓我看看。`） 針對診斷者而言，這並不是一種懷疑，而只是一種真實而有用的需求，以便讓他們看到的是與你看到的原始證據儘可能一致的東西，而不是你的猜測與歸納的結論。所以，大方地展示給我們看吧！"},"401":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-for-private-email","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-for-private-email","type":"page","content":"別要求使用私人電郵回覆","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧","正在提問時"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-for-private-email"},"402":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-for-private-email-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-for-private-email","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-for-private-email#公開討論能提高答案質量","content":"公開討論能提高答案質量"},"403":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-for-private-email-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-for-private-email","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-for-private-email#有限例外你負責整理","content":"有限例外：你負責整理"},"404":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-for-private-email-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-for-private-email","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-for-private-email","content":"黑客們認為問題的解決過程應該公開、透明，此過程中如果更有經驗的人注意到不完整或者不當之處，最初的回覆才能夠、也應該被糾正。同時，作為提供幫助者可以得到一些獎勵，獎勵就是他的能力和學識被其他同行看到。"},"405":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-for-private-email-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-for-private-email","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-for-private-email#公開討論能提高答案質量","content":"當你要求私下回復時，這個過程和獎勵都被中止。別這樣做，讓**回覆者**來決定是否私下回答 —— 如果他真這麼做了，通常是因為他認為問題編寫太差或者太膚淺，以至於不可能使其他人產生興趣。"},"406":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-for-private-email-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-for-private-email","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-for-private-email#公開討論能提高答案質量","content":"公開回復有幾個好處：別人可以糾正錯誤答案，後來者可以搜索到解決方案，參與者也能從討論中學習。私下回復則把這些價值都切斷了。"},"407":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-for-private-email-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-for-private-email","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-for-private-email#有限例外你負責整理","content":"這條規則存在一條有限的例外，如果你確信提問可能會引來大量雷同的回覆時，那麼這個神奇的提問句會是`向我發電郵，我將為論壇歸納這些回覆`。試著將郵件列表或新聞群組從洪水般的雷同回覆中解救出來是非常有禮貌的 —— 但你必須信守諾言。"},"408":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-for-private-email-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-for-private-email","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-for-private-email#有限例外你負責整理","content":"如果你這樣承諾，就要真的把收到的信息整理回公開討論中。否則，你只是把社區知識吸走，並沒有回饋任何東西。"},"409":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework","type":"page","content":"別問自己的家庭作業","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧","正在提問時"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework"},"410":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework#作業的目的就是讓你練習","content":"作業的目的就是讓你練習"},"411":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework#去更合適的新手渠道","content":"去更合適的新手渠道"},"412":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework","content":"黑客們很擅長分辨哪些問題是家庭作業式的問題；因為我們中的大多數都曾自己解決這類問題。同樣，這些問題得由**你**來搞定，你會從中學到東西。你可以要求給點提示，但別要求得到完整的解決方案。"},"413":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework#作業的目的就是讓你練習","content":"家庭作業式問題並不限於學校作業。任何本質上要求你通過練習來掌握概念、完成推理或寫出實現的問題，都屬於這一類。別人直接給你完整答案，只會剝奪你學習的過程。"},"414":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework#作業的目的就是讓你練習","content":"可以問："},"415":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework#作業的目的就是讓你練習","content":"`我對題意的理解是否正確？`"},"416":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework#作業的目的就是讓你練習","content":"`我這個思路卡在某一步，是否有明顯誤區？`"},"417":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework#作業的目的就是讓你練習","content":"`我應該複習哪部分概念？`"},"418":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework#作業的目的就是讓你練習","content":"不要問："},"419":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework-9","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework#作業的目的就是讓你練習","content":"`誰能直接給我完整代碼？`"},"420":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework-10","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework#作業的目的就是讓你練習","content":"`把答案發我一下。`"},"421":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework-11","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework#作業的目的就是讓你練習","content":"`明天要交，幫我做完。`"},"422":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework-12","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework#去更合適的新手渠道","content":"如果你懷疑自己碰到了一個家庭作業式的問題，但仍然無法解決，試試在用戶群組，論壇或（最後一招）在項目的**用戶**郵件列表或論壇中提問。儘管黑客們**會**看出來，但一些有經驗的用戶也許仍會給你一些提示。"},"423":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework-13","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/donnot-ask-homework#去更合適的新手渠道","content":"即使在那裡，也要展示你已經嘗試過什麼。請求提示和請求代做，是完全不同的兩件事。"},"424":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/humble-not-substitute-homewoek","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/humble-not-substitute-homewoek","type":"page","content":"低聲下氣不能代替你的功課","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧","正在提問時"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/humble-not-substitute-homewoek"},"425":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/humble-not-substitute-homewoek-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/humble-not-substitute-homewoek","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/humble-not-substitute-homewoek#自貶不會讓問題更清楚","content":"自貶不會讓問題更清楚"},"426":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/humble-not-substitute-homewoek-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/humble-not-substitute-homewoek","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/humble-not-substitute-homewoek#新手也要認真提問","content":"新手也要認真提問"},"427":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/humble-not-substitute-homewoek-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/humble-not-substitute-homewoek","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/humble-not-substitute-homewoek","content":"有些人明白他們不該粗魯或傲慢的提問並要求得到答覆，但他們選擇另一個極端 —— 低聲下氣：`我知道我只是個可悲的新手，一個失敗者，但...`。這既使人困擾，也沒有用，尤其是伴隨著與實際問題含糊不清的描述時更令人反感。"},"428":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/humble-not-substitute-homewoek-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/humble-not-substitute-homewoek","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/humble-not-substitute-homewoek#自貶不會讓問題更清楚","content":"低聲下氣看似謙虛，實際會把注意力從問題本身轉移到你的情緒上。回答者需要的是事實、背景、目標和嘗試記錄，不是你對自己的評價。"},"429":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/humble-not-substitute-homewoek-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/humble-not-substitute-homewoek","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/humble-not-substitute-homewoek#自貶不會讓問題更清楚","content":"別用原始靈長類動物的把戲來浪費你我的時間。取而代之的是，儘可能清楚地描述背景條件和你的問題情況。這比低聲下氣更好地定位了你的位置。"},"430":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/humble-not-substitute-homewoek-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/humble-not-substitute-homewoek","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/humble-not-substitute-homewoek#自貶不會讓問題更清楚","content":"更好的表達是：`我是第一次使用這個庫，已經讀過入門文檔和 FAQ，但仍不理解下面這個錯誤。` 這既說明了你的經驗水平，也提供了有效背景。"},"431":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/humble-not-substitute-homewoek-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/humble-not-substitute-homewoek","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/humble-not-substitute-homewoek#新手也要認真提問","content":"有時網頁論壇會設有專為新手提問的版面，如果你真的認為遇到了初學者的問題，到那去就是了，但一樣別那麼低聲下氣。"},"432":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/humble-not-substitute-homewoek-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/humble-not-substitute-homewoek","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/humble-not-substitute-homewoek#新手也要認真提問","content":"新手身份不是問題，拒絕做功課才是問題。坦誠說明自己在哪裡不懂，然後給出你已經嘗試過的東西，比反覆道歉更有用。"},"433":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions","type":"page","content":"正在提問時","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧","正在提問時"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions"},"434":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions#提問時的核心原則","content":"提問時的核心原則"},"435":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions#如何閱讀本章","content":"如何閱讀本章"},"436":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions","content":"真正開始提問時，你要做的不只是把問題發出去。你需要選擇合適的場合、寫清楚標題、使用可讀格式、提供事實、描述目標，並讓回答者能快速判斷自己是否幫得上忙。"},"437":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions#提問時的核心原則","content":"當你提出問題的時候，請先表明你已經做過準備。這能幫助別人判斷你不是一個不勞而獲、隨手浪費他人時間的提問者。如果你還能說明自己在準備過程中**學到了什麼**，效果會更好；我們更樂於回答那些表現出能從答案中繼續學習的人。"},"438":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions#提問時的核心原則","content":"一個好的問題通常具備這些特徵："},"439":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions#提問時的核心原則","content":"發在正確的社區或討論區。"},"440":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions#提問時的核心原則","content":"標題能概括目標、環境和異常。"},"441":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions#提問時的核心原則","content":"正文格式清楚，方便引用和回覆。"},"442":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions#提問時的核心原則","content":"描述事實，而不是隻給猜測。"},"443":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions-9","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions#提問時的核心原則","content":"說明目標，而不是隻描述你卡住的步驟。"},"444":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions-10","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions#提問時的核心原則","content":"展示你已經搜索、閱讀、嘗試和排除過什麼。"},"445":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions-11","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions#如何閱讀本章","content":"本章的每一節都處理提問時的一個具體動作：選論壇、寫標題、描述問題、貼代碼、避免無效句式、保持禮貌等。你不必一次記住所有規則，但在真正發問前，至少應該逐項檢查一遍。"},"446":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions-12","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions#如何閱讀本章","content":"提問質量不是靠客氣話堆出來的，而是靠準確的信息、明確的邊界和可協作的態度建立起來的。"},"447":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time","type":"page","content":"按時間先後列出問題","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧","正在提問時"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time"},"448":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time#記錄從哪裡開始","content":"記錄從哪裡開始"},"449":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time#調試信息要適量","content":"調試信息要適量"},"450":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time#長問題先給摘要","content":"長問題先給摘要"},"451":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time","content":"問題發生前的一系列操作，往往就是對找出問題最有幫助的線索。因此，你的說明裡應該包含你的操作步驟，以及機器和軟件的反應，直到問題發生。在命令行處理的情況下，提供一段操作記錄（例如運行腳本工具所生成的），並引用相關的若干行（如 20 行）記錄會非常有幫助。"},"452":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time#記錄從哪裡開始","content":"時間順序不需要從你安裝系統那天開始。它應該從“與問題可能相關的第一步”開始，例如最近一次升級、配置變更、依賴安裝、數據導入、命令執行或重啟。"},"453":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time#記錄從哪裡開始","content":"一個有用的時間線通常包含："},"454":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time#記錄從哪裡開始","content":"你做了什麼。"},"455":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time#記錄從哪裡開始","content":"系統返回了什麼。"},"456":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time#記錄從哪裡開始","content":"你接著嘗試了什麼。"},"457":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time-9","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time#記錄從哪裡開始","content":"問題第一次出現在哪裡。"},"458":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time-10","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time#記錄從哪裡開始","content":"之後你如何確認它仍然存在。"},"459":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time-11","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time#調試信息要適量","content":"如果掛掉的程序有診斷選項（如 -v 的詳述開關），試著選擇這些能在記錄中增加調試信息的選項。記住，`多`不等於`好`。試著選取適當的調試級別以便提供有用的信息而不是讓讀者淹沒在垃圾中。"},"460":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time-12","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time#調試信息要適量","content":"一大段未經篩選的日誌會增加閱讀成本。更好的做法是保留完整日誌的鏈接或附件，同時在正文裡引用最相關的幾十行，並說明它們為什麼重要。"},"461":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time-13","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time#長問題先給摘要","content":"如果你的說明很長（如超過四個段落），在開頭簡述問題，接下來再按時間順序詳述會有所幫助。這樣黑客們在讀你的記錄時就知道該注意哪些內容了。"},"462":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time-14","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/list-problems-by-time#長問題先給摘要","content":"摘要可以很短，例如：`升級到 2.4.1 後，導入 CSV 會在第三步報 UnicodeDecodeError；回退到 2.3.8 後恢復正常。下面是完整時間線。` 這樣的開頭能讓回答者先建立整體判斷，再進入細節。"},"463":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/make-questions-easily","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/make-questions-easily","type":"page","content":"使問題容易回覆","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧","正在提問時"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/make-questions-easily"},"464":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/make-questions-easily-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/make-questions-easily","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/make-questions-easily#不要把回覆成本轉嫁給別人","content":"不要把回覆成本轉嫁給別人"},"465":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/make-questions-easily-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/make-questions-easily","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/make-questions-easily#論壇裡不要要求郵件回覆","content":"論壇裡不要要求郵件回覆"},"466":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/make-questions-easily-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/make-questions-easily","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/make-questions-easily","content":"以`請將你的回覆發送到……`來結束你的問題多半會使你得不到回答。如果你覺得花幾秒鐘在郵件客戶端設置一下回復地址都麻煩，我們也覺得花幾秒鐘思考你的問題更麻煩。如果你的郵件程序不支持這樣做，換個好點的；如果是操作系統不支持這種郵件程序，也換個好點的。"},"467":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/make-questions-easily-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/make-questions-easily","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/make-questions-easily#不要把回覆成本轉嫁給別人","content":"回答者願意花時間思考你的問題，已經是在幫你。不要再要求他們繞過正常討論渠道、複製到私人地址、單獨通知你，或者用額外步驟滿足你的收信習慣。"},"468":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/make-questions-easily-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/make-questions-easily","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/make-questions-easily#不要把回覆成本轉嫁給別人","content":"如果你需要郵件提醒，請配置自己的客戶端或論壇通知，而不是讓每個回覆者替你處理。"},"469":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/make-questions-easily-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/make-questions-easily","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/make-questions-easily#論壇裡不要要求郵件回覆","content":"在論壇，要求通過電子郵件回覆是非常無禮的，除非你認為回覆的信息可能比較敏感（有人會為了某些未知的原因，只讓你而不是整個論壇知道答案）。如果你只是想在有人回覆討論串時得到電子郵件提醒，可以要求網頁論壇發送給你。幾乎所有論壇都支持諸如`追蹤此討論串`、`有回覆時發送郵件提醒`等功能。"},"470":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/make-questions-easily-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/make-questions-easily","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/make-questions-easily#論壇裡不要要求郵件回覆","content":"問題在哪裡公開提出，答案通常也應該在哪裡公開留下。這樣才能讓後來的人搜索、引用和補充。"},"471":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/never-write-urgent","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/never-write-urgent","type":"page","content":"不要在標題寫`緊急`","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧","正在提問時"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/never-write-urgent"},"472":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/never-write-urgent-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/never-write-urgent","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/never-write-urgent#你的緊急不等於社區的緊急","content":"你的緊急不等於社區的緊急"},"473":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/never-write-urgent-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/never-write-urgent","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/never-write-urgent#少數例外也要謹慎","content":"少數例外也要謹慎"},"474":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/never-write-urgent-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/never-write-urgent","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/never-write-urgent#更好的寫法","content":"更好的寫法"},"475":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/never-write-urgent-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/never-write-urgent","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/never-write-urgent","content":"這是你的問題，不是我們的。宣稱`緊急`極有可能事與願違：大多數黑客會直接刪除無禮和自私地企圖即時引起關注的問題。更嚴重的是，`緊急`這個字（或是其他企圖引起關注的標題）通常會被垃圾信過濾器過濾掉 —— 你希望能看到你問題的人可能永遠也看不到。"},"476":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/never-write-urgent-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/never-write-urgent","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/never-write-urgent#你的緊急不等於社區的緊急","content":"對你來說，系統無法啟動、作業快截止、客戶正在等待，都可能非常緊急。但對陌生的回答者來說，這並不會自動製造義務。標題裡寫 `緊急`，通常只會傳達一種信息：你希望別人把你的時間壓力放在自己的事情前面。"},"477":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/never-write-urgent-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/never-write-urgent","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/never-write-urgent#少數例外也要謹慎","content":"有半個例外的情況是，如果你是在一些很高調，會使黑客們興奮的地方，也許值得這樣去做。在這種情況下，如果你有時間壓力，也很有禮貌地提到這點，人們也許會有興趣回答快一點。"},"478":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/never-write-urgent-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/never-write-urgent","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/never-write-urgent#少數例外也要謹慎","content":"當然，這風險很大，因為黑客們興奮的點多半與你的不同。譬如從 NASA 國際空間站（International Space Station）發這樣的標題沒有問題，但用自我感覺良好的慈善行為或政治原因發肯定不行。事實上，張貼諸如`緊急：幫我救救這個毛茸茸的小海豹！`肯定讓你被黑客忽略或惹惱他們，即使他們認為毛茸茸的小海豹很重要。"},"479":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/never-write-urgent-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/never-write-urgent","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/never-write-urgent#更好的寫法","content":"如果確實有時間限制，可以在正文裡平實說明，而不是用標題搶注意力。例如：`這個問題影響今晚的發佈；如果沒人能及時回覆，我會先回滾到上一版本。` 這比 `緊急！！！` 更成熟，也讓別人知道你有備用方案。"},"480":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/never-write-urgent-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/never-write-urgent","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/never-write-urgent#更好的寫法","content":"如果你覺得這點很不可思議，最好再把這份指南剩下的內容多讀幾遍，直到你弄懂了再發文。"},"481":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-more-words-but-essence","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-more-words-but-essence","type":"page","content":"話再多而不在精","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧","正在提問時"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-more-words-but-essence"},"482":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-more-words-but-essence-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-more-words-but-essence","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-more-words-but-essence#信息要足夠但不要堆砌","content":"信息要足夠，但不要堆砌"},"483":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-more-words-but-essence-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-more-words-but-essence","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-more-words-but-essence#最小化問題的三個價值","content":"最小化問題的三個價值"},"484":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-more-words-but-essence-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-more-words-but-essence","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-more-words-but-essence#一個實用標準","content":"一個實用標準"},"485":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-more-words-but-essence-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-more-words-but-essence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-more-words-but-essence","content":"你需要提供精確有內容的信息。這並不是要求你簡單的把成堆的出錯代碼或者資料完全轉錄到你的提問中。如果你有龐大而複雜的測試樣例能重現程序掛掉的情境，儘量將它剪裁得越小越好。"},"486":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-more-words-but-essence-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-more-words-but-essence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-more-words-but-essence#信息要足夠但不要堆砌","content":"“詳細”不等於“把所有東西都貼上來”。日誌、配置、代碼、截圖和錯誤信息都應該經過篩選。你需要保留能支持診斷的事實，刪掉和問題無關的噪聲。"},"487":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-more-words-but-essence-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-more-words-but-essence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-more-words-but-essence#信息要足夠但不要堆砌","content":"如果問題可以用 20 行代碼復現，就不要貼整個項目。如果錯誤只出現在最後 30 行日誌裡，就不要把幾萬行日誌直接塞進正文。"},"488":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-more-words-but-essence-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-more-words-but-essence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-more-words-but-essence#最小化問題的三個價值","content":"這樣做的用處至少有三點。\n第一，表現出你為簡化問題付出了努力，這可以使你得到回答的機會增加；\n第二，簡化問題使你更有可能得到**有用**的答案；\n第三，在精煉你的 bug 報告的過程中，你很可能就自己找到了解決方法或權宜之計。"},"489":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-more-words-but-essence-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-more-words-but-essence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-more-words-but-essence#一個實用標準","content":"在發問前問自己：回答者是否能用你給出的材料復現或理解問題，同時又不必在大量無關內容裡搜尋線索？如果不能，就繼續裁剪、整理和標註重點。"},"490":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily","type":"page","content":"別動輒聲稱找到 Bug","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧","正在提問時"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily"},"491":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily#可能是-bug需要證據","content":"“可能是 Bug”需要證據"},"492":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily#指控會影響對話氣氛","content":"指控會影響對話氣氛"},"493":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily#用謙遜但清楚的方式報告","content":"用謙遜但清楚的方式報告"},"494":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily","content":"當你在使用軟件中遇到問題，除非你非常、**非常**的有根據，不要動輒聲稱找到了 Bug。提示：除非你能提供解決問題的源代碼補丁，或者提供迴歸測試來表明前一版本中行為不正確，否則你都多半不夠完全確信。這同樣適用在網頁和文件，如果你（聲稱）發現了文件的`Bug`，你應該能提供相應位置的修正或替代文件。"},"495":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily#可能是-bug需要證據","content":"請記得，還有其他許多用戶沒遇到你發現的問題，否則你在閱讀文件或搜索網頁時就應該發現了（你在抱怨前已經做了這些，是吧？）。這也意味著很有可能是你弄錯了而不是軟件本身有問題。"},"496":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily#可能是-bug需要證據","content":"如果你懷疑是 Bug，請儘量提供："},"497":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily#可能是-bug需要證據","content":"最小復現步驟。"},"498":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily#可能是-bug需要證據","content":"當前版本和歷史版本的行為差異。"},"499":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily#可能是-bug需要證據","content":"明確的預期行為依據，例如文檔或規範。"},"500":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily-9","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily#可能是-bug需要證據","content":"日誌、測試用例、補丁或失敗的迴歸測試。"},"501":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily-10","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily#指控會影響對話氣氛","content":"編寫軟件的人總是非常辛苦地使它儘可能完美。如果你聲稱找到了 Bug，也就是在質疑他們的能力，即使你是對的，也有可能會冒犯到其中某部分人。當你在標題中嚷嚷著有`Bug`時，這尤其嚴重。"},"502":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily-11","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily#用謙遜但清楚的方式報告","content":"提問時，即使你私下非常確信已經發現一個真正的 Bug，最好寫得像是**你**做錯了什麼。如果真的有 Bug，你會在回覆中看到這點。這樣做的話，如果真有 Bug，維護者就會向你道歉，這總比你惹惱別人然後欠別人一個道歉要好一點。"},"503":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily-12","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/not-say-find-bug-easily#用謙遜但清楚的方式報告","content":"比如，把 `這個庫有 Bug` 改成 `在這個最小示例中，2.1.0 的行為與文檔描述不一致；我是否遺漏了某個配置？`。這種寫法既保留了問題的嚴重性，也給維護者留下判斷空間。"},"504":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem","type":"page","content":"精確描述問題","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧","正在提問時"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem"},"505":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem#需要寫清楚的信息","content":"需要寫清楚的信息"},"506":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem#預先回答可能的追問","content":"預先回答可能的追問"},"507":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem#可復現環境尤其重要","content":"可復現環境尤其重要"},"508":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem#延伸閱讀","content":"延伸閱讀"},"509":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem","content":"精確描述問題，是讓別人能夠繼續診斷的前提。你不需要一次寫成論文，但必須提供足夠事實，讓回答者不用先反覆追問最基本的信息。"},"510":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem#需要寫清楚的信息","content":"仔細、清楚地描述你的問題或 Bug 的症狀。"},"511":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem#需要寫清楚的信息","content":"描述問題發生的環境（機器配置、操作系統、應用程序、以及相關的信息），提供經銷商的發行版和版本號（如：`Fedora Core 4`、`Slackware 9.1`等）。"},"512":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem#需要寫清楚的信息","content":"描述在提問前你是怎樣去研究和理解這個問題的。"},"513":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem#需要寫清楚的信息","content":"描述在提問前為確定問題而採取的診斷步驟。"},"514":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem-9","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem#需要寫清楚的信息","content":"描述最近做過什麼可能相關的硬件或軟件變更。"},"515":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem-10","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem#需要寫清楚的信息","content":"儘可能地提供一個可以`重現這個問題的可控環境`的方法。"},"516":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem-11","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem#預先回答可能的追問","content":"儘量去揣測一個黑客會怎樣反問你，在你提問之前預先將黑客們可能提出的問題回答一遍。"},"517":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem-12","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem#預先回答可能的追問","content":"你可以把自己放在回答者的位置上想一想："},"518":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem-13","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem#預先回答可能的追問","content":"我知道問題在哪個版本、哪臺機器、哪種配置下發生嗎？"},"519":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem-14","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem#預先回答可能的追問","content":"我知道它是穩定復現，還是偶爾出現嗎？"},"520":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem-15","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem#預先回答可能的追問","content":"我知道提問者已經排除了哪些原因嗎？"},"521":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem-16","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem#預先回答可能的追問","content":"我能照著描述復現同樣的問題嗎？"},"522":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem-17","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem#預先回答可能的追問","content":"如果答案是否定的，就繼續補充信息。"},"523":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem-18","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem#可復現環境尤其重要","content":"以上幾點中，當你報告的是你認為可能在代碼中的問題時，給黑客一個可以重現你的問題的環境尤其重要。當你這麼做時，你得到有效的回答的機會和速度都會大大的提升。"},"524":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem-19","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem#可復現環境尤其重要","content":"“可復現”不一定意味著完整複製你的生產環境。一個最小示例、一段觸發錯誤的配置、一組輸入數據，或者一條明確的命令，都可能足以讓別人觀察同樣的現象。"},"525":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem-20","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/precisely-describe-problem#延伸閱讀","content":"Simon Tatham 寫過一篇名為《如何有效地報告Bug》的出色文章。強力推薦你也讀一讀。"},"526":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence","type":"page","content":"去掉無意義的提問句","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧","正在提問時"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence"},"527":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence#為什麼這類句子沒有價值","content":"為什麼這類句子沒有價值"},"528":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence#換成具體請求","content":"換成具體請求"},"529":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence#避免只會得到是否的問題","content":"避免只會得到“是/否”的問題"},"530":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence","content":"避免用無意義的話結束提問，例如`有人能幫我嗎？`或者`這有答案嗎？`。"},"531":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence#為什麼這類句子沒有價值","content":"首先：如果你對問題的描述不是很好，這樣問更是畫蛇添足。"},"532":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence#為什麼這類句子沒有價值","content":"其次：由於這樣問是畫蛇添足，黑客們會很厭煩你 —— 而且通常會用邏輯上正確，但毫無意義的回答來表示他們的蔑視， 例如：`沒錯，有人能幫你`或者`不，沒答案`。"},"533":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence#為什麼這類句子沒有價值","content":"這類句子沒有提供任何診斷信息，也沒有說明你希望別人做什麼。它們只是在要求別人先承諾會不會幫你。"},"534":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence#換成具體請求","content":"與其寫 `有人能幫我嗎？`，不如寫："},"535":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence#換成具體請求","content":"`我應該優先檢查哪一層？`"},"536":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence-9","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence#換成具體請求","content":"`這個錯誤是否說明依賴版本不兼容？`"},"537":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence-10","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence#換成具體請求","content":"`這個最小示例是否足以說明問題？`"},"538":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence-11","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence#換成具體請求","content":"`有沒有我遺漏的常見配置項？`"},"539":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence-12","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence#換成具體請求","content":"這些問題能讓回答者直接進入技術判斷。"},"540":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence-13","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence#避免只會得到是否的問題","content":"一般來說，避免用 `是或否`、`對或錯`、`有或沒有`類型的問句，除非你想得到是或否類型的回答。"},"541":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence-14","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/remove-questional-sentence#避免只會得到是否的問題","content":"如果你真正需要的是解釋、方向或診斷建議，就不要把問題寫成只能回答“是”或“不是”的形式。"},"542":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow","type":"page","content":"Stack Overflow","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧","正在提問時"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow"},"543":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow#先搜索已有答案","content":"先搜索已有答案"},"544":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow#提問時遵守平臺習慣","content":"提問時遵守平臺習慣"},"545":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow#選擇正確的網站","content":"選擇正確的網站"},"546":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow","content":"搜索，*然後*在 Stack Exchange 問。"},"547":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow","content":"近年來，Stack Exchange 社區已經成為回答技術及其他問題的主要渠道，尤其是那些開放源碼的項目。"},"548":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow#先搜索已有答案","content":"因為 Google 索引是即時的，在看 Stack Exchange 之前先在 Google 搜索。有很高的幾率某人已經問了一個類似的問題，而且 Stack Exchange 網站們往往會是搜索結果中最前面幾個。如果你在 Google 上沒有找到任何答案，你再到特定相關主題的網站去找。用標籤（Tag）搜索能讓你更縮小你的搜索結果。"},"549":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow#先搜索已有答案","content":"搜索時可以同時使用錯誤信息、庫名、語言名、版本號和關鍵 API 名稱。Stack Exchange 的歷史問題很多，重複問題通常不會受到歡迎。"},"550":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow#提問時遵守平臺習慣","content":"如果你還是找不到任何對你的問題有用的內容，請把你的問題發在與它最相關的網站上。提問的時候請善用格式化工具，尤其注意為代碼添加格式，並且添加相關的標籤（特別是編程語言、操作系統或庫/包的名稱）。當有人要求你提供更多相關信息時，請編輯你的貼子來補充它們\\[譯註：而不是發一個回帖或回答！]。如果你覺得一個答案對你有幫助，點擊向上的箭頭來為它投票；如果一個答案提供了問題的正確解決方案，點擊投票按鈕下方的對勾來將它標記為正解。"},"551":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow#提問時遵守平臺習慣","content":"這不是形式主義。格式、標籤、編輯補充、投票和接受答案，都是 Stack Exchange 用來維護知識庫質量的機制。"},"552":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow-9","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow#選擇正確的網站","content":"Stack Exchange 已經成長到超過一百個網站，以下是最常用的幾個站："},"553":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow-10","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow#選擇正確的網站","content":"Super User 是問一些通用的電腦問題，如果你的問題跟代碼或是寫程序無關，只是一些網絡連線之類的，請到這裡。"},"554":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow-11","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow#選擇正確的網站","content":"Stack Overflow 是問寫程序有關的問題。"},"555":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow-12","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow#選擇正確的網站","content":"Server Fault 是問服務器和網管相關的問題。"},"556":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow-13","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/stack-overflow#選擇正確的網站","content":"如果你把問題發錯站點，即使問題本身不錯，也可能被關閉或遷移。先確認站點範圍，比發完以後再解釋要有效得多。"},"557":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence","type":"page","content":"用清晰、正確、精準的語句","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧","正在提問時"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence"},"558":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence#語言質量會影響別人對你的判斷","content":"語言質量會影響別人對你的判斷"},"559":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence#避免製造閱讀障礙","content":"避免製造閱讀障礙"},"560":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence#非母語提問時怎麼處理","content":"非母語提問時怎麼處理"},"561":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence#最後的標準","content":"最後的標準"},"562":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence","content":"我們從經驗中發現，粗心的提問者通常也會粗心地寫程序與思考（我敢打包票）。回答粗心大意者的問題很不值得，我們寧願把時間耗在別處。"},"563":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence#語言質量會影響別人對你的判斷","content":"正確的拼寫、標點符號和大小寫是很重要的。一般來說，如果你覺得這樣做很麻煩，不想在乎這些，那我們也覺得麻煩，不想在乎你的提問。花點額外的精力斟酌一下字句，用不著太僵硬與正式 —— 事實上，黑客文化很看重能準確地使用非正式、俚語和幽默的語句。但它**必須很**準確，而且有跡象表明你是在思考和關注問題。"},"564":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence#語言質量會影響別人對你的判斷","content":"清晰表達不是為了顯得文雅，而是為了減少誤解。一個標點混亂、大小寫隨意、句子斷裂的問題，會讓別人懷疑你在代碼、日誌和測試上也同樣粗心。"},"565":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence#避免製造閱讀障礙","content":"正確地拼寫、使用標點和大小寫，不要將`its`混淆為`it's`，`loose`搞成`lose`或者將`discrete`弄成`discreet`。不要**全部用大寫**，這會被視為無禮的大聲嚷嚷（全部小寫也好不到哪去，因為不易閱讀。Alan Cox 也許可以這樣做，但你不行）。"},"566":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence#避免製造閱讀障礙","content":"更白話的說，如果你寫得像是個半文盲\\[譯註：小白]，那多半得不到理睬。也不要使用即時通信中的簡寫或火星文，如將`的`簡化為`d`會使你看起來像一個為了少打幾個鍵而省字的小白。更糟的是，如果像個小孩似地鬼畫符那絕對是在找死，可以肯定沒人會理你（或者最多是給你一大堆指責與挖苦）。"},"567":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence-9","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence#非母語提問時怎麼處理","content":"如果在使用非母語的論壇提問，你可以犯點拼寫和語法上的小錯，但決不能在思考上馬虎（沒錯，我們通常能弄清兩者的分別）。同時，除非你知道回覆者使用的語言，否則請使用英語書寫。繁忙的黑客一般會直接刪除用他們看不懂的語言寫的消息。在網絡上英語是通用語言，用英語書寫可以將你的問題在尚未被閱讀就被直接刪除的可能性降到最低。"},"568":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence-10","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence#非母語提問時怎麼處理","content":"如果英文是你的外語（Second language），提示潛在回覆者你有潛在的語言困難是很好的：\n\\[譯註：以下附上原文以供使用]"},"569":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence-11","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence#非母語提問時怎麼處理","content":"> English is not my native language; please excuse typing errors."},"570":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence-12","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence#非母語提問時怎麼處理","content":"英文不是我的母語，請原諒我的錯字或語法。"},"571":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence-13","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence#非母語提問時怎麼處理","content":"> If you speak $LANGUAGE, please email/PM me;\n> I may need assistance translating my question."},"572":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence-14","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence#非母語提問時怎麼處理","content":"如果你說**某語言**，請向我發電郵/私信；"},"573":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence-15","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence#非母語提問時怎麼處理","content":"我需要有人協助我翻譯我的問題。"},"574":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence-16","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence#非母語提問時怎麼處理","content":"> I am familiar with the technical terms,\n> but some slang expressions and idioms are difficult for me."},"575":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence-17","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence#非母語提問時怎麼處理","content":"我對技術名詞很熟悉，但對於俗語或是特別用法不甚瞭解。"},"576":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence-18","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence#非母語提問時怎麼處理","content":"> I've posted my question in $LANGUAGE and English.\n> I'll be glad to translate responses, if you only use one or the other."},"577":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence-19","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence#非母語提問時怎麼處理","content":"我把我的問題用**某語言**和英文寫出來。"},"578":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence-20","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence#非母語提問時怎麼處理","content":"如果你只用其中的一種語言回答，我會樂意將回復翻譯成為你使用的語言。"},"579":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence-21","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-correctly-sentence#最後的標準","content":"語言可以不完美，但必須看得出你認真。回答者通常能區分“外語不熟”和“思考混亂”，也能區分“表達樸素”和“完全不尊重閱讀者”。"},"580":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format","type":"page","content":"使用標準的文件格式發送問題","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧","正在提問時"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format"},"581":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format#讓正文容易閱讀和引用","content":"讓正文容易閱讀和引用"},"582":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format#避免奇怪編碼和封閉格式","content":"避免奇怪編碼和封閉格式"},"583":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format#不要用裝飾干擾內容","content":"不要用裝飾干擾內容"},"584":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format#歸根結底降低閱讀成本","content":"歸根結底：降低閱讀成本"},"585":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format","content":"如果你人為地將問題搞得難以閱讀，它多半會被忽略，人們更願讀易懂的問題，所以："},"586":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format#讓正文容易閱讀和引用","content":"使用純文字而不是 HTML (關閉 HTML 並不難）。"},"587":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format#讓正文容易閱讀和引用","content":"使用 MIME 附件通常是可以的，前提是真正有內容（譬如附帶的源代碼或 patch），而不僅僅是郵件程序生成的模板（譬如只是信件內容的拷貝）。"},"588":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format#讓正文容易閱讀和引用","content":"不要發送一段文字只是一行句子但自動換行後會變成多行的郵件（這使得回覆部分內容非常困難）。設想你的讀者是在 80 個字符寬的終端機上閱讀郵件，最好設置你的換行分割點小於 80 字。"},"589":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format#讓正文容易閱讀和引用","content":"但是，對一些特殊的文件**不要**設置固定寬度（譬如日誌文件拷貝或會話記錄）。數據應該原樣包含，讓回覆者有信心他們看到的是和你看到的一樣的東西。"},"590":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format-9","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format#避免奇怪編碼和封閉格式","content":"在英語論壇中，不要使用`Quoted-Printable` MIME 編碼發送消息。這種編碼對於張貼非 ASCII 語言可能是必須的，但很多郵件程序並不支持這種編碼。當它們處理換行時，那些文本中四處散佈的`=20`符號既難看也分散注意力，甚至有可能破壞內容的語意。"},"591":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format-10","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format#避免奇怪編碼和封閉格式","content":"絕對，**永遠**不要指望黑客們閱讀使用封閉格式編寫的文檔，像微軟公司的 Word 或 Excel 文件等。大多數黑客對此的反應就像有人將還在冒熱氣的豬糞倒在你家門口時你的反應一樣。即便他們能夠處理，他們也很厭惡這麼做。"},"592":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format-11","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format#避免奇怪編碼和封閉格式","content":"如果你從使用 Windows 的電腦發送電子郵件，關閉微軟愚蠢的`智能引號`功能 （從\\[選項] > \\[校訂] > \\[自動校正選項]，勾選掉`智能引號`單選框），以免在你的郵件中到處散佈垃圾字符。"},"593":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format-12","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format#不要用裝飾干擾內容","content":"在論壇，勿濫用`表情符號`和`HTML`功能（當它們提供時）。一兩個表情符號通常沒有問題，但花哨的彩色文本傾向於使人認為你是個無能之輩。過濫地使用表情符號、色彩和字體會使你看來像個傻笑的小姑娘。這通常不是個好主意，除非你只是對性而不是對答案感興趣。"},"594":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format-13","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format#不要用裝飾干擾內容","content":"如果你使用圖形用戶界面的郵件程序（如微軟公司的 Outlook 或者其它類似的），注意它們的默認設置不一定滿足這些要求。大多數這類程序有基於選單的`查看源代碼`命令，用它來檢查發送文件夾中的郵件，以確保發送的是純文本文件同時沒有一些奇怪的字符。"},"595":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format-14","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-easy-to-read-file-format#歸根結底降低閱讀成本","content":"格式不是小事。可複製的文本、原樣保留的日誌、清楚的換行和開放格式，都會讓別人更容易引用、測試和回覆你的問題。你讓問題越容易處理，別人越可能願意處理。"},"596":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines","type":"page","content":"使用有意義且描述明確的標題","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧","正在提問時"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines"},"597":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines#標題應該描述問題而不是情緒","content":"標題應該描述問題，而不是情緒"},"598":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines#好標題也方便後來者搜索","content":"好標題也方便後來者搜索"},"599":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines#回覆時也要維護標題","content":"回覆時也要維護標題"},"600":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines#網頁論壇的差異","content":"網頁論壇的差異"},"601":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines","content":"在郵件列表、新聞群組或論壇中，大約 50 字以內的標題是抓住資深專家注意力的好機會。別用喋喋不休的`幫幫忙`、`跪求`、`急`（更別說`救命啊！！！！`這樣讓人反感的話，用這種標題會被條件反射式地忽略）來浪費這個機會。不要妄想用你的痛苦程度來打動我們，而應該是在這點空間中使用極簡單扼要的描述方式來提出問題。"},"602":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines#標題應該描述問題而不是情緒","content":"一個好標題範例是`目標 —— 差異`式的描述，許多技術支持組織就是這樣做的。在`目標`部分指出是哪一個或哪一組東西有問題，在`差異`部分則描述與期望的行為不一致的地方。"},"603":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines#標題應該描述問題而不是情緒","content":"> 蠢問題：救命啊！我的筆記本電腦不能正常顯示了！"},"604":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines#標題應該描述問題而不是情緒","content":"> 聰明問題：X.org 6.8.1 的鼠標指針會變形，某牌顯卡 MV1005 芯片組。"},"605":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines#標題應該描述問題而不是情緒","content":"> 更聰明問題：X.org 6.8.1 的鼠標指針，在某牌顯卡 MV1005 芯片組環境下 - 會變形。"},"606":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines-9","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines#標題應該描述問題而不是情緒","content":"編寫`目標 —— 差異` 式描述的過程有助於你組織對問題的細緻思考。是什麼被影響了？ 僅僅是鼠標指針或者還有其它圖形？只在 X.org 的 X 版中出現？或只是出現在 6.8.1 版中？ 是針對某牌顯卡芯片組？或者只是其中的 MV1005 型號？ 一個黑客只需瞄一眼就能夠立即明白你的環境**和**你遇到的問題。"},"607":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines-10","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines#好標題也方便後來者搜索","content":"總而言之，請想像一下你正在一個只顯示標題的存檔討論串（Thread）索引中查尋。讓你的標題更好地反映問題，可使下一個搜索類似問題的人能夠關注這個討論串，而不用再次提問相同的問題。"},"608":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines-11","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines#回覆時也要維護標題","content":"如果你想在回覆中提出問題，記得要修改內容標題，以表明你是在問一個問題， 一個看起來像 `Re: 測試` 或者 `Re: 新 bug` 的標題很難引起足夠重視。另外，在不影響連貫性之下，適當引用並刪減前文的內容，能給新來的讀者留下線索。"},"609":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines-12","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines#回覆時也要維護標題","content":"對於討論串，不要直接點擊回覆來開始一個全新的討論串，這將限制你的觀眾。因為有些郵件閱讀程序，比如 mutt ，允許用戶按討論串排序並通過摺疊討論串來隱藏消息，這樣做的人永遠看不到你發的消息。"},"610":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines-13","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines#回覆時也要維護標題","content":"僅僅改變標題還不夠。mutt 和其它一些郵件閱讀程序還會檢查郵件標題以外的其它信息，以便為其指定討論串。所以寧可發一個全新的郵件。"},"611":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines-14","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines#網頁論壇的差異","content":"在網頁論壇上，好的提問方式稍有不同，因為討論串與特定的信息緊密結合，並且通常在討論串外就看不到裡面的內容，故通過回覆提問，而非改變標題是可接受的。不是所有論壇都允許在回覆中出現分離的標題，而且這樣做了基本上沒有人會去看。不過，通過回覆提問，這本身就是曖昧的做法，因為它們只會被正在查看該標題的人讀到。所以，除非你**只想**在該討論串當前活躍的人群中提問，不然還是另起爐灶比較好。"},"612":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines-15","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-meaningful-headlines#網頁論壇的差異","content":"一個可靠的判斷標準是：只看標題時，陌生讀者能否知道你在什麼環境下遇到了什麼異常。如果不能，標題就還不夠好。"},"613":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list","type":"page","content":"使用項目郵件列表","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧","正在提問時"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list"},"614":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list#為什麼要發到列表","content":"為什麼要發到列表"},"615":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list#用戶列表和開發者列表不要混用","content":"用戶列表和開發者列表不要混用"},"616":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list#何時升級到開發者渠道","content":"何時升級到開發者渠道"},"617":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list#找不到列表時再聯繫維護者","content":"找不到列表時再聯繫維護者"},"618":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list","content":"當某個項目提供開發者郵件列表時，要向列表而不是其中的個別成員提問，即使你確信他能最好地回答你的問題。查一查項目的文件和首頁，找到項目的郵件列表並使用它。有幾個很好的理由支持我們採用這種辦法："},"619":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list#為什麼要發到列表","content":"任何好到需要向個別開發者提出的問題，也將對整個項目群組有益。反之，如果你認為自己的問題對整個項目群組來說太愚蠢，那這也不能成為騷擾個別開發者的理由。"},"620":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list#為什麼要發到列表","content":"向列表提問可以分散開發者的負擔，個別開發者（尤其是項目領導人）也許太忙以至於沒法回答你的問題。"},"621":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list#為什麼要發到列表","content":"大多數郵件列表都會被存檔，那些被存檔的內容將被搜索引擎索引。如果你向列表提問並得到解答，將來其他人可以通過網頁搜索找到你的問題和答案，也就不用再次發問了。"},"622":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list#為什麼要發到列表","content":"如果某些問題經常被問到，開發者可以利用此信息來改進說明文件或軟件本身，以使其更清楚。如果只是私下提問，就沒有人能看到最常見問題的完整場景。"},"623":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list-9","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list#為什麼要發到列表","content":"公開列表讓問題、答案、糾正和後續總結都留在項目知識庫裡。私下發給某個開發者，通常只會增加對方負擔，並減少其他人受益的機會。"},"624":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list-10","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list#用戶列表和開發者列表不要混用","content":"如果一個項目既有“用戶”也有“開發者”（或“黑客”）郵件列表或論壇，而你又不會動到那些源代碼，那麼就向“用戶”列表或論壇提問。不要假設自己會在開發者列表中受到歡迎，那些人多半會將你的提問視為干擾他們開發的噪音。"},"625":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list-11","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list#用戶列表和開發者列表不要混用","content":"開發者列表通常用於討論實現、補丁、設計、迴歸和發佈。普通使用問題放在那裡，往往會顯得你沒有尊重列表用途。"},"626":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list-12","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list#何時升級到開發者渠道","content":"然而，如果你**確信**你的問題很特別，而且在“用戶”列表或論壇中幾天都沒有回覆，可以試試前往“開發者”列表或論壇發問。建議你在張貼前最好先暗地裡觀察幾天以瞭解那裡的行事方式（事實上這是參與任何私有或半私有列表的好主意）"},"627":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list-13","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list#何時升級到開發者渠道","content":"升級提問時，要說明你已經在用戶渠道問過、等待了多久、得到了哪些信息，以及為什麼你認為這個問題可能需要開發者判斷。"},"628":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list-14","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list#找不到列表時再聯繫維護者","content":"如果你找不到一個項目的郵件列表，而只能查到項目維護者的電子郵件地址，儘管向他發信。即使是在這種情況下，也別假設（項目）郵件列表不存在。在你的電子郵件中，請陳述你已經試過但沒有找到合適的郵件列表，也提及你不反對將自己的郵件轉發給他人（許多人認為，即使沒什麼秘密，私人電子郵件也不應該被公開。通過允許將你的電子郵件轉發他人，你給了相應人員處置你郵件的選擇）。"},"629":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list-15","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/use-project-email-list#找不到列表時再聯繫維護者","content":"這能讓維護者更容易把問題轉給合適的人，也避免他們因為隱私顧慮而無法公開你的問題。"},"630":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc","type":"page","content":"網站和 IRC 論壇","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧","正在提問時"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc"},"631":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc#新手問題先找用戶支持渠道","content":"新手問題先找用戶支持渠道"},"632":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc#發行版問題先問發行版社區","content":"發行版問題先問發行版社區"},"633":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc#發問前搜索論壇內部","content":"發問前搜索論壇內部"},"634":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc#選擇同步或異步渠道","content":"選擇同步或異步渠道"},"635":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc","content":"本地的用戶群組（user group），或者你所用的 Linux 發行版本也許正在宣傳他們的網頁論壇或 IRC 頻道，並提供新手幫助（在一些非英語國家，新手論壇很可能還是郵件列表），這些都是開始提問的好地方，特別是當你覺得遇到的也許只是相對簡單或者很普通的問題時。有廣告贊助的 IRC 頻道是公開歡迎提問的地方，通常可以即時得到回應。"},"636":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc#新手問題先找用戶支持渠道","content":"用戶群組、發行版論壇、網頁論壇和 IRC 頻道，往往比開發者郵件列表更適合入門問題。那裡的人更熟悉常見安裝、配置、環境差異和使用誤區，也更願意處理“我剛開始用”的問題。"},"637":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc#發行版問題先問發行版社區","content":"事實上，如果程序出的問題只發生在特定 Linux 發行版提供的版本（這很常見），最好先去該發行版的論壇或郵件列表中提問，再到程序本身的論壇或郵件列表提問。（否則）該項目的黑客可能僅僅回覆“使用**我們的**版本”。"},"638":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc#發行版問題先問發行版社區","content":"發行版常常會修改編譯選項、補丁、默認配置和依賴版本。上游項目不一定知道這些差異，因此先問發行版社區通常更有效。"},"639":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc#發問前搜索論壇內部","content":"在任何論壇發文以前，先確認一下有沒有搜索功能。如果有，就試著搜索一下問題的幾個關鍵詞，也許這會有幫助。如果在此之前你已做過通用的網頁搜索（你也該這樣做），還是再搜索一下論壇，搜索引擎有可能沒來得及索引此論壇的全部內容。"},"640":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc-9","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc#發問前搜索論壇內部","content":"論壇內部搜索能發現搜索引擎還沒收錄、或被登錄權限擋住的討論。先搜索，也能讓你瞭解這個社區喜歡怎樣描述問題。"},"641":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc-10","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc#選擇同步或異步渠道","content":"通過論壇或 IRC 頻道來提供用戶支持服務有增長的趨勢，電子郵件則大多為項目開發者間的交流而保留。所以最好先在論壇或 IRC 中尋求與該項目相關的協助。"},"642":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc-11","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc#選擇同步或異步渠道","content":"在使用 IRC 的時候，首先最好不要發佈很長的問題描述，有些人稱之為頻道洪水。最好通過一句話的問題描述來開始聊天。"},"643":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc-12","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/website-and-irc#選擇同步或異步渠道","content":"IRC 更適合快速澄清和短互動；論壇更適合長問題、日誌、代碼和後續總結。選擇渠道時，先想清楚你的問題需要即時對話，還是需要可搜索、可沉澱的長文本。"},"644":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code","type":"page","content":"詢問有關代碼的問題時","breadcrumbs":["提問的智慧","正在提問時"],"tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code"},"645":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code-0","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code#給出入口點","content":"給出入口點"},"646":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code-1","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code#提供最小復現","content":"提供最小復現"},"647":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code-2","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code#即使縮不小也要展示努力","content":"即使縮不小，也要展示努力"},"648":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code-3","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code#如果你想要代碼審查","content":"如果你想要代碼審查"},"649":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code-4","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code","content":"如果沒有提示別人應該從何入手，別要求他人幫你調試有問題的代碼。張貼幾百行的代碼，然後說一聲：`它不能工作`會讓你完全被忽略。只貼幾十行代碼，然後說一句：`在第七行以後，我期待它顯示 <x>，但實際出現的是 <y>`比較有可能讓你得到回應。"},"650":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code-5","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code#給出入口點","content":"別人看你的代碼時，需要知道該從哪裡開始看、期望行為是什麼、實際行為是什麼。沒有這些信息，代碼越多，越像是在把排查工作整體轉交給別人。"},"651":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code-6","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code#給出入口點","content":"一個更好的代碼問題通常包含："},"652":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code-7","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code#給出入口點","content":"最小可運行代碼片段。"},"653":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code-8","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code#給出入口點","content":"運行方式或編譯命令。"},"654":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code-9","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code#給出入口點","content":"預期輸出和實際輸出。"},"655":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code-10","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code#給出入口點","content":"錯誤發生的位置。"},"656":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code-11","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code#給出入口點","content":"你已經嘗試過的修改。"},"657":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code-12","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code#提供最小復現","content":"最有效描述程序問題的方法是提供最精簡的 Bug 展示測試用例（bug-demonstrating test case）。什麼是最精簡的測試用例？那是問題的縮影；一小個程序片段能**剛好**展示出程序的異常行為，而不包含其他令人分散注意力的內容。怎麼製作最精簡的測試用例？如果你知道哪一行或哪一段代碼會造成異常的行為，複製下來並加入足夠重現這個狀況的代碼（例如，足以讓這段代碼能被編譯/直譯/被應用程序處理）。如果你無法將問題縮減到一個特定區塊，就複製一份代碼並移除不影響產生問題行為的部分。總之，測試用例越小越好（查看話不在多而在精一節）。"},"658":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code-13","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code#即使縮不小也要展示努力","content":"一般而言，要得到一段相當精簡的測試用例並不太容易，但永遠先嚐試這樣做是一個好習慣。這種方式可以幫助你瞭解如何自行解決這個問題 —— 而且即使你的嘗試不成功，黑客們也會看到你在嘗試取得答案的過程中付出了努力，這可以讓他們更願意與你合作。"},"659":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code-14","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code#如果你想要代碼審查","content":"如果你只是想讓別人幫忙審查（Review）一下代碼，在信的開頭就要說出來，並且一定要提到你認為哪一部分特別需要關注以及為什麼。"},"660":{"id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code-15","page_id":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/zh-tw/docs/when-questions/when-ask-code#如果你想要代碼審查","content":"“請幫我看看”太寬泛。更好的說法是：`我想確認這個錯誤處理是否會吞掉異常`，或者 `這段鎖的使用是否可能導致死鎖`。明確審查目標，別人才能有效投入。"}},"count":660},"sorting":{"language":"english","sortableProperties":["content","page_id","type","url"],"sortablePropertiesWithTypes":{"content":"string","page_id":"string","type":"string","url":"string"},"sorts":{"content":{"docs":{"1":240,"2":266,"3":359,"4":413,"5":579,"6":241,"7":196,"8":611,"9":559,"10":95,"11":198,"12":517,"13":644,"14":227,"15":363,"16":365,"17":645,"18":353,"19":550,"20":283,"21":272,"22":180,"23":578,"24":436,"25":537,"26":629,"27":498,"28":263,"29":273,"30":262,"31":161,"32":637,"33":636,"34":547,"35":224,"36":323,"37":587,"38":502,"39":340,"40":154,"41":156,"42":152,"43":151,"44":592,"45":242,"46":210,"47":35,"48":602,"49":374,"50":267,"51":400,"52":401,"53":394,"54":393,"55":395,"56":555,"57":367,"58":325,"59":123,"60":651,"61":493,"62":477,"63":608,"64":534,"65":590,"66":42,"67":44,"68":33,"69":36,"70":593,"71":291,"72":465,"73":543,"74":522,"75":2,"76":167,"77":191,"78":639,"79":25,"80":64,"81":610,"82":20,"83":70,"84":600,"85":26,"86":67,"87":130,"88":21,"89":51,"90":431,"91":27,"92":71,"93":464,"94":22,"95":65,"96":599,"97":265,"98":125,"99":620,"100":127,"101":657,"102":92,"103":297,"104":173,"105":105,"106":494,"107":521,"108":582,"109":293,"110":16,"111":14,"112":11,"113":13,"114":28,"115":171,"116":12,"117":17,"118":15,"119":321,"120":299,"121":558,"122":199,"123":622,"124":111,"125":285,"126":609,"127":603,"128":108,"129":121,"130":565,"131":561,"132":456,"133":591,"134":186,"135":356,"136":355,"137":350,"138":348,"139":115,"140":433,"141":418,"142":632,"143":302,"144":544,"145":122,"146":147,"147":342,"148":217,"149":364,"150":305,"151":430,"152":90,"153":378,"154":